1
00:00:00,837 --> 00:00:13,626


2
00:00:14,905 --> 00:00:26,246
-=The Last Fantasy=-
翻译：Fatreo & keaya
校对：Disenchanted
双语：Diksonhe

3
00:00:28,405 --> 00:00:31,366
宇宙立方已经苏醒
The Tesseract has awakened.

4
00:00:33,202 --> 00:00:38,159
它正在一个渺小世界里，人类的世界
It is on a little world, a human world.

5
00:00:38,874 --> 00:00:42,207
人类想利用它的能量
They would wield its power,

6
00:00:42,586 --> 00:00:48,256
他们不会成功只有我们的盟友才能利用它
but our ally knows its workings as they never will.

7
00:00:49,802 --> 00:00:52,885
他将作为先锋
He is ready to lead

8
00:00:53,097 --> 00:00:58,517
而我们智塔利人大军将紧随其后
and our force, our Chitauri, will follow.

9
00:01:00,146 --> 00:01:02,517
给他一个地球
A world will be his.

10
00:01:02,731 --> 00:01:05,850
我们拥有宇宙
The universe, yours.

11
00:01:06,068 --> 00:01:11,940
至于人类，除了等死，还能做什么？
And the humans,what can they do but burn?

12
00:01:26,172 --> 00:01:27,250
全体人员注意
All personnel,

13
00:01:27,423 --> 00:01:29,711
疏散命令已获确认
the evacuation order has been confirmed.

14
00:01:29,424 --> 00:01:30,675


15
00:01:30,862 --> 00:01:33,051
（联合暗能量行动）
(DIRECTING AGENTS)

16
00:02:01,624 --> 00:02:03,081
情况有多糟糕？
How bad is it?

17
00:02:03,292 --> 00:02:06,577
长官，最糟的就是我们不知道情况
That's the problem, sir. We don't know.

18
00:02:10,174 --> 00:02:13,090
绍韦博士四小时前侦测到立方发出的能量波
Dr. Selvig read an energy surge from the Tesseract four hours ago.

19
00:02:13,219 --> 00:02:15,091
宇航局未批准绍韦进入测试阶段
NASA didn't authorise Selvig to go to test phase.

20
00:02:15,304 --> 00:02:17,461
他没有测试，当时他根本不在房间里
He wasn't testing it.He wasn't even in the room.

21
00:02:17,681 --> 00:02:18,676
是自动触发的
Spontaneous event.

22
00:02:18,849 --> 00:02:19,963
宇宙立方自行启动？
It just turned itself on?

23
00:02:20,184 --> 00:02:21,214
现在的能级达到多少了？
Where are the energy levels now?

24
00:02:21,435 --> 00:02:23,593
攀升中，绍韦没能把它停下来,我们因此下令撤离
Climbing. When Selvig couldn't shut it down, we ordered evac.

25
00:02:23,813 --> 00:02:25,010
完全撤离还要多久？
How long to get everyone out?

26
00:02:25,231 --> 00:02:26,558
半小时应该够了
Campus should be clear in the next half-hour.

27
00:02:26,774 --> 00:02:28,018
再快点
Do better.

28
00:02:28,984 --> 00:02:30,941
长官，撤离也许是徒劳无益的
Sir, evacuation may be futile.

29
00:02:31,153 --> 00:02:32,528
那我应该让他们都回去歇着？
We should tell them to go back to sleep?

30
00:02:32,738 --> 00:02:34,944
如果我们无法控制宇宙立方的力量
If we can't control the Tesseract's energy,

31
00:02:35,157 --> 00:02:37,481
也就不会有「安全距离」一说了
there may not be a minimum safe distance.

32
00:02:37,618 --> 00:02:40,445
你去确保二阶段原型机的安全转移
I need you to make sure the Phase 2 prototypes are shipped out.

33
00:02:38,660 --> 00:02:40,370


34
00:02:40,621 --> 00:02:42,660
长官，真的要优先考虑它们？
Sir, is that really a priority right now?

35
00:02:42,873 --> 00:02:44,580
除非到世界末日
Until such time as the world ends,

36
00:02:44,708 --> 00:02:46,747
否则我们就得这么来
we will act as though it intends to spin on.

37
00:02:47,711 --> 00:02:49,086
把下面的设备都搬走
Clear out the tech below.

38
00:02:49,296 --> 00:02:51,786
二阶段原型机的每一个部件都要装车运走
Every piece of Phase 2 on a truck and gone.

39
00:02:52,007 --> 00:02:53,086
遵命，长官
Yes, sir.

40
00:02:53,509 --> 00:02:54,671
跟我来
With me.

41
00:02:57,763 --> 00:02:58,758
说说情况吧，博士
Talk to me, Doctor.

42
00:03:00,558 --> 00:03:01,932
局长
Director.

43
00:03:02,143 --> 00:03:03,802
我们确切知道的情况有哪些？
Is there anything we know for certain?

44
00:03:04,019 --> 00:03:06,260
宇宙立方不大听话
The Tesseract is misbehaving.

45
00:03:06,480 --> 00:03:09,266
- 你在开玩笑？- 不，我不是开玩笑
- Is that supposed to be funny? - No, it's not funny at all.

46
00:03:09,483 --> 00:03:12,982
宇宙立方不仅被唤醒了，还在自行活动
The Tesseract is not only active, she's behaving.

47
00:03:13,194 --> 00:03:14,189
拔了电源试试？
I assume you pulled the plug.

48
00:03:14,404 --> 00:03:16,111
它自身是个能量源
She's an energy source.

49
00:03:16,322 --> 00:03:19,358
我们关闭了电源，它又重新打开
We turn off the power,she turns it back on.

50
00:03:19,576 --> 00:03:20,654
如果它能级达到峰值
If she reaches peak level...

51
00:03:20,869 --> 00:03:24,284
博士，这不正是我们所需要的吗？利用宇宙的能量
We prepared for this, Doctor. Harnessing energy from space.

52
00:03:24,497 --> 00:03:25,872
但是我们没办法控制
But we don't have the harness.

53
00:03:25,999 --> 00:03:27,278
我们离利用还差得远呢
My calculations are far from complete.

54
00:03:27,834 --> 00:03:30,371
它在释放干扰与辐射
And she's throwing off interference, radiation.

55
00:03:30,587 --> 00:03:32,294
低能级的伽玛射线，没什么危害
Nothing harmful,low levels of gamma radiation.

56
00:03:33,214 --> 00:03:35,040
也许会有危害
That can be harmful.

57
00:03:35,258 --> 00:03:36,668
巴顿探员呢？
Where's Agent Barton?

58
00:03:36,843 --> 00:03:38,550
鹰眼？
The Hawk?

59
00:03:39,429 --> 00:03:41,467
一如既往，在他的鹰巢里
Up in his nest, as usual.

60
00:03:42,932 --> 00:03:44,723
巴顿探员，请回答
Agent Barton, report.

61
00:03:45,602 --> 00:03:46,763
我让你来
I gave you this detail

62
00:03:46,895 --> 00:03:48,471
是希望你能够近距离进行观察
so you could keep a close eye on things.

63
00:03:48,688 --> 00:03:50,062
我站远点看得更清楚
Well, I see better from a distance.

64
00:03:50,273 --> 00:03:52,229
你有看到什么东西激活它了吗？
Have you seen anything that might set this thing off?

65
00:03:52,692 --> 00:03:54,814
博士，能量又达到峰值了
Doctor, it's spiking again.

66
00:03:55,028 --> 00:03:56,402
没有人员进出
No one's come or gone.

67
00:03:56,613 --> 00:03:58,236
绍韦也没问题
And Selvig's clean.

68
00:03:58,448 --> 00:04:00,736
没人与外界联系或传输信息
No contacts, no IMs.

69
00:04:01,242 --> 00:04:03,033
如果有什么扰动，也不来自这端，长官
If there was any tampering, sir,it wasn't at this end.

70
00:04:04,954 --> 00:04:06,329
「来自这端」？
"At this end"?

71
00:04:06,539 --> 00:04:10,370
是啊，立方不是通往宇宙另一端的通道吗？
Yeah, the Cube is a doorway to the other end of space, right?

72
00:04:12,212 --> 00:04:13,491
通道是双向的
Doors open from both sides.

73
00:04:14,255 --> 00:04:15,583
