Please don't.

87
00:06:40,984 --> 00:06:42,181
我还要它呢
I still need that.

88
00:06:42,402 --> 00:06:43,860
没必要把事情弄那么复杂
This doesn't have to get any messier.

89
00:06:44,071 --> 00:06:45,268
