and I am burdened with glorious purpose.

93
00:06:55,415 --> 00:06:56,825
洛基
Loki,

94
00:06:57,334 --> 00:06:58,614
托尔的弟弟
brother of Thor.

95
00:06:58,836 --> 00:07:01,290
你我族类毫无恩怨
We have no quarrel with your people.

96
00:07:01,505 --> 00:07:04,458
蚂蚁与靴子也毫无恩怨
An ant has no quarrel with a boot.

97
00:07:05,050 --> 00:07:06,709
你也打算踩死我们？
Are you planning to step on us?

98
00:07:07,052 --> 00:07:10,135
我给你们带来福音
I come with glad tidings

99
00:07:11,390 --> 00:07:13,298
为整个世界带来解脱
of a world made free.

100
00:07:13,684 --> 00:07:14,679
怎么解脱？
Free from what?

101
00:07:14,893 --> 00:07:16,221
从自由中解脱
Freedom.

102
00:07:16,770 --> 00:07:19,391
自由是生命中最大的谎言
Freedom is life's great lie.

103
00:07:19,606 --> 00:07:23,021
当你内心接受了这观念
Once you accept that, in your heart,

104
00:07:24,028 --> 00:07:25,363


105
00:07:27,531 --> 00:07:29,404
你就将获得安宁
you will know peace.

106
00:07:29,700 --> 00:07:32,154
你嘴上说「安宁」
Yeah, you say "peace,"

107
00:07:32,369 --> 00:07:34,195
但我觉得你想表达的却恰恰相反
I kind of think you mean the other thing.

108
00:07:34,413 --> 00:07:36,903
长官，霍利局长在拖延时间
Sir, Director Fury is stalling.

109
00:07:37,124 --> 00:07:38,451
这地方马上就要爆炸了
This place is about to blow

110
00:07:38,584 --> 00:07:40,291
我们会被压在几十米的岩石下
and drop a hundred feet of rock on us.

111
00:07:41,795 --> 00:07:42,825
他想活埋了我们
He means to bury us.

112
00:07:43,046 --> 00:07:44,160
像古代的法老一样
Like the pharaohs of old.

113
00:07:44,381 --> 00:07:46,337
他说得对，传送门正在自我坍塌
He's right. The portal is collapsing in on itself.

114
00:07:46,550 --> 00:07:48,755
离临界状态只有两分钟了
We've got maybe two minutes before this goes critical.

115
00:07:49,136 --> 00:07:50,131
好吧
Well, then.

116
00:07:50,388 --> 00:07:51,973


117
