我要用这些车
I need these vehicles.

118
00:08:11,074 --> 00:08:13,196
- 那是谁？ - 我也不知道
- Who's that? - They didn't tell me.

119
00:08:16,413 --> 00:08:17,657
希尔！
Hill!

120
00:08:18,081 --> 00:08:19,361
能听到吗？
Do you CODY?

121
00:08:20,084 --> 00:08:21,411
巴顿叛变了
Barton has turned.

122
00:08:22,003 --> 00:08:22,879


123
00:08:34,473 --> 00:08:37,307
他们拿走了宇宙立方！拦下他们！
They have the Tesseract! Shut them down!

124
00:09:09,508 --> 00:09:11,219


125
00:09:13,719 --> 00:09:15,925
快走，别管它了，快走！
Okay, let's go. No, leave it. Go!

126
00:09:32,405 --> 00:09:34,527
楼上撤离完毕了，长官，你得走了
We're clear upstairs, sir. You need to go.

127
00:09:57,515 --> 00:09:58,516


128
00:10:26,043 --> 00:10:26,752


129
00:10:52,528 --> 00:10:53,404


130
00:11:06,499 --> 00:11:07,826
局长？
Director?

131
00:11:08,167 --> 00:11:09,660
霍利局长，能听到吗？
Director Fury, do you copy?

132
00:11:09,877 --> 00:11:12,165
宇宙立方已落入敌手
The Tesseract is with a hostile force.

133
00:11:12,422 --> 00:11:14,828
有人受伤，希尔，你那边呢？
I have men down. Hill?

134
00:11:15,174 --> 00:11:17,047
还有很多人被埋
A lot of men still under.

135
00:11:17,260 --> 00:11:18,967
不清楚有多少生还者
I don't know how many survivors.

136
00:11:19,177 --> 00:11:20,339
发布命令
Sound a general call.

137
00:11:20,554 --> 00:11:22,261
所有没参加救援工作的人员
I want every living soul not working rescue

138
00:11:22,389 --> 00:11:23,384
都去寻找那个箱子
looking for that briefcase.

139
00:11:23,598 --> 00:11:24,629
收到
Roger that.

140
00:11:24,850 --> 00:11:28,134
古逊，赶回基地，这是七级事件
Coulson, get back to base. This is a Level Seven.

141
00:11:29,229 --> 00:11:30,806
我们的战争
As of right now,

142
00:11:31,022 --> 00:11:32,480
就此开始
we are at war.

143
00:11:34,192 --> 00:11:35,472
我们该做什么？
What do we do?

144
00:11:40,800 --> 00:11:48,428
复仇者联盟

