171
00:13:28,476 --> 00:13:29,643


172
00:13:31,977 --> 00:13:33,434
找她的
It's for her.

173
00:13:36,898 --> 00:13:38,178
听仔细了
You listen carefully

174
00:13:38,316 --> 00:13:40,889
你在114号萨伦斯基广场三楼
You're at 1-14 Silensky Plaza, 3rd floor.

175
00:13:41,153 --> 00:13:43,275
有架F22在八英里外待命
We have an F-22 exactly eight miles out.

176
00:13:44,156 --> 00:13:46,112
让那女人接电话，否则不等你跑到大厅
Put the woman on the phone or I will blow up the block

177
00:13:46,324 --> 00:13:48,363
我就炸平整条街
before you can make the lobby.

178
00:13:54,833 --> 00:13:56,955
- 我们需要你回来 - 开玩笑哪？我在工作
- We need you to come in. - Are you kidding? I'm working.

179
00:13:57,169 --> 00:13:58,448
这边情况更加危急
This takes precedence.

180
00:13:58,670 --> 00:14:00,294
我都审问了一半了
I'm in the middle of an interrogation.

181
00:14:00,463 --> 00:14:02,253
那蠢货什么都招了
This moron is giving me everything.

182
00:14:02,673 --> 00:14:05,293
