Oh, I've got Stark. You get the big guy.

201
00:15:17,334 --> 00:15:18,335


202
00:15:24,758 --> 00:15:26,385


203
00:15:36,604 --> 00:15:37,605


204
00:15:37,688 --> 00:15:38,606


205
00:15:38,811 --> 00:15:39,806
你是谁？
Who are you?

206
00:15:40,271 --> 00:15:41,349
快出去！
Get out!

207
00:15:41,480 --> 00:15:43,970
会传染的！
There is sickness here!

208
00:15:44,108 --> 00:15:45,103
你是医生吗？
You're a doctor.

209
00:15:45,112 --> 00:15:46,113


210
00:15:46,819 --> 00:15:48,098
我爸爸昏迷不醒了
My father's not waking up!

211
00:15:48,237 --> 00:15:50,063
他发烧了，还一直呻吟
He has a fever and he's moaning

212
00:15:50,197 --> 00:15:51,275
但眼睛却睁不开
but his eyes won't open.

213
00:15:51,407 --> 00:15:52,402
慢点
Slow down.

214
00:15:53,951 --> 00:15:55,029
我爸爸
My father...

215
00:15:57,413 --> 00:15:58,408
像他们一样？
Like them?

216
00:15:59,418 --> 00:16:01,170


217
00:16:02,418 --> 00:16:03,662
求你了
Please.

218
00:16:08,218 --> 00:16:10,054


219
00:16:30,863 --> 00:16:33,151
你该先收钱的，班纳
You should've got paid up front, Banner.

220
00:16:33,365 --> 00:16:36,063
对一个需要远离压力的人来说
You know, for a man who's supposed to be avoiding stress

221
00:16:36,285 --> 00:16:39,534
你居然选择住在这种地方
you picked a hell of a place to settle.

222
00:16:41,290 --> 00:16:43,495
我靠的并不是远离压力
Avoiding stress isn't the secret.

223
00:16:43,708 --> 00:16:46,198
那是靠什么，瑜伽？
Then what is it? Yoga?

224
00:16:47,378 --> 00:16:50,544
把我引到郊区，聪明的决定
You brought me to the edge of the city. Smart.

225
00:16:51,132 --> 00:16:55,176
我猜我已被重兵包围了
I assume the whole place is surrounded.

226
00:16:55,637 --> 00:16:57,011
只有你我二人
Just you and me.

227
00:16:58,264 --> 00:17:00,303
你的小演员哪？
And your actress buddy?

228
00:17:00,517 --> 00:17:02,473
她也是个间谍？那么小就入行了？
Is she a spy, too? They start that young?

229
00:17:02,894 --> 00:17:04,138
我入行时也不大
I did.

230
00:17:04,354 --> 00:17:05,384
你是谁？
Who are you?

231
00:17:05,605 --> 00:17:06,719
娜塔莎·罗曼诺夫
Natasha Romanoff.

232
00:17:10,068 --> 00:17:11,395
你是来取我性命的吗，罗曼诺夫小姐？
Are you here to kill me, Ms. Romanoff?

233
00:17:11,611 --> 00:17:14,315
这可不是一般人能完成的任务
Because that's not going to work out for everyone.

234
00:17:14,531 --> 00:17:16,985
当然不是，我是代表神盾局来的
No, of course not. I'm here on behalf of S.H.I.E.L.D.

235
00:17:18,743 --> 00:17:20,236
神盾局
S.H.I.E.L.D.

236
00:17:22,038 --> 00:17:23,033
他们怎么找到我的？
How did they find me?

237
00:17:23,206 --> 00:17:24,830
我们一直关注着你，博士
We never lost you, Doctor.

238
00:17:25,041 --> 00:17:26,036
只是保持了距离
We've kept our distance.

239
00:17:26,251 --> 00:17:29,241
还帮你挡下了些不速之客
Even helped keep some other interested parties off your scent.

240
00:17:29,754 --> 00:17:30,749
为什么这样？
Why?

241
00:17:30,880 --> 00:17:33,251
尼克·霍利似乎很信任你
Nick Fury seems to trust you.

242
00:17:33,466 --> 00:17:35,090
但现在我们需要你的加入
But now we need you to come in.

243
00:17:36,052 --> 00:17:37,925
如果我拒绝呢？
What if I say no?

244
00:17:38,138 --> 00:17:40,260
我会说服你的
I'll persuade you.

245
00:17:42,392 --> 00:17:46,720
要是「另一个我」说不呢？
And what if the other guy says no?

246
00:17:47,439 --> 00:17:49,062
你们已经一年多没出事了
You've been more than a year without an incident.

247
00:17:49,274 --> 00:17:51,846
你总想让这个纪录延续吧
I don't think you want to break that streak.

248
00:17:54,070 --> 00:17:56,691
好吧，我并非时时刻刻都能控制住自己
Well, I don't every time get what I want.

249
00:17:57,740 --> 00:17:59,946
博士，一场全球性的大灾变很可能就要降临
Doctor, we're facing a potential global catastrophe.

250
00:18:00,785 --> 00:18:03,904
这些正是我一直试图远离的
Well, those I actively try to avoid.

251
00:18:04,247 --> 00:18:06,286
这东西
This

252
00:18:06,499 --> 00:18:08,870
就是宇宙立方
is the Tesseract.

253
00:18:09,085 --> 00:18:11,871
它有足以夷平整个地球的能量
It has the potential energy to wipe out the planet.

254
00:18:14,716 --> 00:18:16,873
霍利想让我怎么做，把它吃了？
What does Fury want me to do, swallow it?

255
00:18:17,093 --> 00:18:19,548
它被人夺走了，霍利希望你可以找到它
He wants you to find it. It's been taken.

256
00:18:20,388 --> 00:18:24,551
它释放的伽玛射线强度太弱 我们无法追踪
It emits a gamma signature that's too weak for us to trace.

257
00:18:24,768 --> 00:18:27,684
没有人比你更懂伽玛射线了
There's no one that knows gamma radiation like you do.

258
00:18:27,896 --> 00:18:30,682
所以我才来找你
If there was, that's where I'd be.

259
00:18:31,274 --> 00:18:33,431
那么说，霍利不是派你来抓怪物的？
So, Fury isn't after the monster?

260
00:18:33,651 --> 00:18:34,895
至少他没这么说
Not that he's told me.

261
00:18:35,111 --> 00:18:37,269
他什么都跟你说了？
And he tells you everything?

262
00:18:37,947 --> 00:18:39,322
和霍利谈谈吧，他现在需要你
Talk to Fury. He needs you on this.

263
00:18:39,449 --> 00:18:40,479
需要把我关笼子里？
He needs me in a cage?

264
00:18:40,617 --> 00:18:41,611
没人打算把你关在…
No one's going to put you in a...

265
00:18:41,785 --> 00:18:42,779
别骗我了！
Stop lying to me!

266
00:18:42,748 --> 00:18:43,916


267
00:18:46,998 --> 00:18:49,618
对不起，又失态了
I'm sorry. That was mean.

268
00:18:50,585 --> 00:18:52,742
我只是想看看你的反应
I just wanted to see what you'd do.

269
00:18:53,963 --> 00:18:56,916
咱们好好说话
Why don't we do this the easy way

270
00:18:57,133 --> 00:18:58,377
你也别用枪指着我
where you don't use that

271
00:18:58,593 --> 00:19:02,506
那家伙也就不会添乱
and the other guy doesn't make a mess.

272
00:19:03,306 --> 00:19:04,586
好吗？
Okay?

273
00:19:05,600 --> 00:19:06,927
娜塔莎？
Natasha?

274
00:19:12,607 --> 00:19:13,637
退后
Stand down.

275
00:19:14,609 --> 00:19:16,150
一切顺利
We're good here.

276
00:19:17,987 --> 00:19:19,529
这叫「只有你我二人」
"Just you and me."

277
00:19:21,699 --> 00:19:24,272
这有些过火了，局长
This is out of line, Director.

278
00:19:24,494 --> 00:19:26,901
你试图运用你不能控制的力量
You're dealing with forces you can't control.

279
00:19:27,329 --> 00:19:30,779
议员先生，你上过战场吗，真枪实弹的？
You ever been in a war, Councilman? In a firefight?

280
00:19:30,999 --> 00:19:33,786
你觉得绝对控制存在吗？
Did you feel an overabundance of control?

281
00:19:34,002 --> 00:19:37,370
你是说亚斯加特正与我们行星开战？
You're saying that this Asgard is declaring war on our planet?

282
00:19:37,506 --> 00:19:40,126
不是亚斯加特，只是洛基
Not Asgard. Loki.

283
00:19:40,342 --> 00:19:43,128
肯定不止他一人，另一个呢？
He can't be working alone.What about the other one?

284
00:19:43,262 --> 00:19:44,292
他的哥哥
His brother.

285
00:19:44,430 --> 00:19:46,468
根据我们的情报，他并非我们的敌人
Our intelligence says Thor is not a hostile

286
00:19:46,682 --> 00:19:47,677
但他离我们太远
but he's worlds away.

287
00:19:47,850 --> 00:19:49,640
我们也不能指望他帮忙
We can't depend on him to help, either.

288
00:19:49,768 --> 00:19:50,763
全得看我们自己
It's up to us.

289
00:19:50,894 --> 00:19:53,515
这就是你需要全力研发第二阶段的原因
Which is why you should be focusing on Phase 2.

290
00:19:53,689 --> 00:19:54,968
它正是为了应对这种…
It was designed for exactly this...

291
00:19:55,190 --> 00:19:58,356
二阶段尚未完成，敌人已大军压境
Phase 2 isn't ready. Our enemy is.

292
00:19:58,610 --> 00:20:00,152
我们需要应急反应部队
We need a response team.

293
00:20:00,362 --> 00:20:02,650
复仇者联盟计划早已停止
The Avengers Initiative was shut down.

294
00:20:02,865 --> 00:20:04,655
我不是说复仇者联盟
This isn't about the Avengers.

295
00:20:04,867 --> 00:20:05,980
我看过那份名单
We've seen the list.

296
00:20:06,201 --> 00:20:08,407
你拥有世界上最精锐的特工组织
You're running the world's greatest covert security network

297
00:20:08,537 --> 00:20:10,160
却还要把人类的命运
and you're going to leave the fate of the human race

298
00:20:10,330 --> 00:20:11,574
置于那群怪胎手中
to a handful of freaks.

299
00:20:11,707 --> 00:20:13,615
人类的命运不会被握在任何人手中
I'm not leaving anything to anyone.

300
00:20:13,834 --> 00:20:16,039
我们确实需要应急反应部队
We need a response team.

301
00:20:16,295 --> 00:20:18,999
他们也许性情孤僻，互有不合
These people may be isolated, unbalanced even

302
00:20:19,214 --> 00:20:23,377
但只要引导得当，他们正是我们现在最急需的
but I believe with the right push they can be exactly what we need.

303
00:20:23,677 --> 00:20:24,957
你确定？
You believe?

304
00:20:25,179 --> 00:20:28,760
感情用事是赢不了战争的，局长
War isn't won by sentiment, Director.

305
00:20:29,475 --> 00:20:32,807
当然，是士兵拼下来的
No, it's won by soldiers.

306
00:20:39,990 --> 00:20:41,658


307
00:20:52,456 --> 00:20:54,246
时间不够了
There's not enough time.

308
00:20:54,458 --> 00:20:55,999
我得让它落入海里
I got to put her in the water!

309
00:21:01,381 --> 00:21:02,412
你不是一个人在战斗
You won't be alone.

310
00:21:03,008 --> 00:21:04,501
我的天啊
Oh, my God.

311
00:21:04,968 --> 00:21:06,130
这家伙竟然还活着！
This guy is still alive!

312
00:21:09,519 --> 00:21:11,104


313
00:21:30,911 --> 00:21:32,653
失眠了？
Trouble sleeping?

314
00:21:33,997 --> 00:21:36,666
我都睡了70年了，长官,早睡够了
I slept for 70 years, sir. I think I've had my fill.

315
00:21:38,210 --> 00:21:42,123
那你应该出门庆祝一下，四处看看
Then you should be out,celebrating, seeing the world.

316
00:21:47,970 --> 00:21:50,804
我被冰封期间，世界正处在战乱中
When I went under, the world was at war.

317
00:21:51,014 --> 00:21:52,840
等我醒来，他们说我们赢了
I wake up, they say we won.

318
00:21:53,559 --> 00:21:55,100
却对我们的损失绝口不提
They didn't say what we lost.

319
00:21:55,686 --> 00:21:58,010
我们一路上也犯了不少错误
We've made some mistakes along the way.

320
00:21:58,439 --> 00:22:00,098
最近就有一些
Some, very recently.

321
00:22:01,650 --> 00:22:02,847
你是带着任务来的吗，长官？
Are you here with a mission, sir?

322
00:22:02,985 --> 00:22:03,980
是的
I am.

323
00:22:04,111 --> 00:22:05,770
想把我融入外面的世界？
Trying to get me back in the world?

324
00:22:06,280 --> 00:22:07,939
想让你拯救外面的世界
Trying to save it.

325
00:22:12,618 --> 00:22:14,610
海德拉的秘密武器
HYDRA'S secret weapon.

326
00:22:13,184 --> 00:22:14,703


327
00:22:14,829 --> 00:22:16,904
这是史塔在找你的时候
Howard Stark fished that out of the ocean

328
00:22:17,039 --> 00:22:18,153
从海里捞上来的
when he was looking for you.

329
00:22:18,708 --> 00:22:20,367
他和我们观点相同
He thought what we think.

330
00:22:20,626 --> 00:22:24,753
宇宙立方是人类开发利用永续能源的关键
The Tesseract could be the key to unlimited sustainable energy.

331
00:22:25,214 --> 00:22:29,045
这正是世界所需要的
That's something the world sorely needs.

332
00:22:30,553 --> 00:22:31,715
谁把它夺走了？
Who took it from you?

333
00:22:31,929 --> 00:22:33,339
洛基
He's called Loki.

334
00:22:33,556 --> 00:22:36,176
他远道而来
He's not from around here.

335
00:22:36,642 --> 00:22:40,050
如果你加入我们，还得给你补补课
There's a lot we'll have to bring you up to speed on if you're in.

336
00:22:40,980 --> 00:22:43,019
不是你不明白
The world has gotten even stranger

337
00:22:43,149 --> 00:22:44,227
这世界变化快
than you already know.

338
00:22:44,734 --> 00:22:47,306
我现在早见怪不怪了
At this point, I doubt anything would surprise me.

339
00:22:47,945 --> 00:22:49,604
你错了，我赌10美元
Ten bucks says you're wrong.

340
00:22:51,365 --> 00:22:55,238
任务报告放在你的公寓了
There's a debriefing packet waiting for you back at your apartment.

341
00:22:57,622 --> 00:22:59,530
关于宇宙立方的情况
Is there anything you can tell us about the Tesseract

342
00:22:59,665 --> 00:23:00,862
你有什么能告诉我们的吗？
that we ought to know now?

343
00:23:01,167 --> 00:23:03,455
你们就不该把它捞出来
You should have left it in the ocean.

344
00:23:04,384 --> 00:23:05,927


345
00:23:12,726 --> 00:23:15,353


346
00:23:36,202 --> 00:23:39,072
我这边搞定了，剩下的就看你了
Good to go on this end. The rest is up to you.

347
00:23:39,288 --> 00:23:40,616
断开与输电线的连接了吗？
You disconnected the transmission lines?

348
00:23:40,748 --> 00:23:41,743
我们脱离了供电网络？
Are we off the grid?

349
00:23:41,874 --> 00:23:45,668
史塔大厦将成为能源自给的标志性建筑
Stark Tower is about to become a beacon of self-sustaining clean energy.

350
00:23:45,795 --> 00:23:49,161
前提是弦反应堆能够替代电网正常供电
Well, assuming the arc reactor takes over and it actually works.

351
00:23:49,549 --> 00:23:50,828
没问题的
I assume.

352
00:23:51,342 --> 00:23:52,337
点亮吧
Light her up.

353
00:23:56,234 --> 00:23:59,843


354
00:23:57,890 --> 00:23:58,885
看起来如何？
How does it look?

355
00:23:59,058 --> 00:24:01,726
像圣诞节一样，但更有我的特色
Like Christmas, but with more me.

356
00:24:01,936 --> 00:24:03,678
我们得在普及公众意识上更进一步才行
We've got to go wider on the public awareness campaign.

357
00:24:03,896 --> 00:24:04,927
你得在传媒上多造势
You need to do some press.

358
00:24:05,565 --> 00:24:06,559
我明天就去华盛顿
I'm in DC tomorrow,

359
00:24:06,732 --> 00:24:08,226
为接下来三座大厦选址
I'm working on the zoning for the next three buildings.

360
00:24:08,401 --> 00:24:10,606
小辣椒，别扫兴，我们期待这一刻已久
Pepper, you're killing me. The moment, remember?

361
00:24:10,820 --> 00:24:11,850
尽情享受现在吧
Enjoy the moment.

362
00:24:12,071 --> 00:24:13,233
进来我们一块享受吧
Get in here and I will.

363
00:24:16,576 --> 00:24:19,492
先生，神盾局的古逊探员来电
Sir, Agent Coulson of S.H.I.E.L.D. is on the line.

364
00:24:20,079 --> 00:24:21,074
说我在外面
I'm not in.

365
00:24:21,748 --> 00:24:23,027
我也的确在外面
I'm actually out.

366
00:24:26,508 --> 00:24:28,510


367
00:24:30,256 --> 00:24:32,876
先生，他坚持要找你
Sir, I'm afraid he's insisting.

368
00:24:33,092 --> 00:24:35,843
长点骨气，佐维斯，我约会呢
Grow a spine, Jarvis. I got a date.

369
00:24:40,391 --> 00:24:43,344
能级保持稳定
Levels are holding steady, I think.

370
00:24:43,561 --> 00:24:45,718
那还用说，我亲自参与的
Of course they are. I was directly involved.

371
00:24:45,938 --> 00:24:47,100
这让我不得不考虑一个问题
Which brings me to my next question.

372
00:24:47,273 --> 00:24:49,229
当个天才感觉如何？
How does it feel to be a genius?

373
00:24:49,441 --> 00:24:51,682
看来我这辈子肯定没机会考虑这个问题了
Well, I really wouldn't know, now would I?

374
00:24:51,902 --> 00:24:56,397
别这样说，你可是我灵感的源泉
What do you mean? All this came from you.

375
00:24:56,615 --> 00:25:00,232
不，这才是一切的源泉
No, all this came from that.

376
00:25:00,452 --> 00:25:02,740
别太谦虚
Give yourself some credit. Please.

377
00:25:02,954 --> 00:25:04,745
史塔大厦就像你的孩子一样
Stark Tower is your baby.

378
00:25:04,956 --> 00:25:07,328
你有12%的功劳
Give yourself 12% of the credit.

379
00:25:07,793 --> 00:25:08,906
12%？
12%?

380
00:25:09,044 --> 00:25:10,157
15%，不能再多了
An argument can be made for 15.

381
00:25:10,295 --> 00:25:11,872
就12%还叫「我的孩子」？
12%? My baby?

382
00:25:12,089 --> 00:25:13,665
毕竟所有的重活都是我干的
Well, I did do all the heavy lifting.

383
00:25:13,799 --> 00:25:15,671
准确地说，重物都是我搬的
Literally, I lifted the heavy things.

384
00:25:15,926 --> 00:25:18,167
对了，说说混乱的安保系统
And, sorry, but the security snafu?

385
00:25:18,303 --> 00:25:19,761
都怪你
- That was on you. - Oh.

386
00:25:19,930 --> 00:25:22,005
- 我的私人电梯 - 你是说我们的电梯？
- My private elevator... - You mean our elevator?

387
00:25:22,224 --> 00:25:24,892
挤满了浑身臭汗的工人
...It was teeming with sweaty workmen.

388
00:25:25,102 --> 00:25:29,602
我会为刚才分功的评论付出代价的，对吧？
I'm going to pay for that comment about percentages in some subtle way later, aren't I?

389
00:25:30,065 --> 00:25:31,262
可没那么简单
It's not going to be that subtle.

390
00:25:31,483 --> 00:25:32,762
这么说吧
I'll tell you what.

391
00:25:32,984 --> 00:25:35,439
下一座大厦上将挂上「宝芝」的大名
The next building is gonna say "Potts" on the tower.

392
00:25:35,654 --> 00:25:37,028
还是写租约上吧
On the lease.

393
00:25:37,948 --> 00:25:40,070
打电话问你妈你能不能留下过夜
Call your mom. Can you bunk over?

394
00:25:40,283 --> 00:25:41,527
先生，您的电话
Sir, the telephone.

395
00:25:41,743 --> 00:25:44,114
我的规程被改写了
I'm afraid my protocols are being overridden.

396
00:25:44,329 --> 00:25:46,285
史塔先生，我有事找你
Mr. Stark, we need to talk.

397
00:25:46,581 --> 00:25:48,906
你正在与东尼·史塔的仿生假体通话
You have reached the life model decoy of Tony Stark.

398
00:25:49,167 --> 00:25:51,123
- 请留言 - 我有急事
- Please leave a message. - This is urgent.

399
00:25:51,336 --> 00:25:53,126
那就快点说
Then leave it urgently.

400
00:25:54,673 --> 00:25:55,786
安保漏洞，你的错
Security breach. It's on you.

401
00:25:56,007 --> 00:25:58,711
- 史塔先生 - 费尔，快请进
- Mr. Stark. - Phil! Come in.

402
00:25:58,885 --> 00:25:59,880
「费尔」？
"Phil"?

403
00:26:00,011 --> 00:26:01,042
我不能久留
I can't stay.

404
00:26:01,263 --> 00:26:02,460
他名叫「探员」
His first name is "Agent."

405
00:26:02,681 --> 00:26:04,304
快请进，我们正在庆祝
Come on in. We're celebrating.

406
00:26:04,516 --> 00:26:06,306
正因此他不能久留
Which is why he can't stay.

407
00:26:06,518 --> 00:26:08,474
请尽快阅读这些资料
We need you to look this over as soon as possible.

408
00:26:08,687 --> 00:26:09,717
我不喜欢别人递给我东西
I don't like being handed things.

409
00:26:09,938 --> 00:26:11,396
没事，我喜欢别人递给我东西
That's fine, because I love to be handed things.

410
00:26:11,606 --> 00:26:12,934
我们换一换
So, let's trade.

411
00:26:14,317 --> 00:26:15,811
谢谢你
Thank you.

412
00:26:17,028 --> 00:26:20,359
正式咨询时间是每隔一周的 周四的早8点到下午5点
Official consulting hours are between 8 and 5 every other Thursday.

413
00:26:20,532 --> 00:26:21,527
我不是来咨询的
This isn't a consultation.

414
00:26:21,658 --> 00:26:22,902
是关于复仇者联盟？
Is this about the Avengers?

415
00:26:23,326 --> 00:26:25,152
我对此一无所知
Which I know nothing about.

416
00:26:25,370 --> 00:26:27,907
我记得复仇者联盟计划早已废弃
The Avengers Initiative was scrapped, I thought.

417
00:26:28,123 --> 00:26:29,497
我连入选资格都没有
And I didn't even qualify.

418
00:26:29,708 --> 00:26:30,703
我也不大清楚
I didn't know that either.

419
00:26:30,876 --> 00:26:33,745
何况我反复无常，偏执自恋
Apparently I'm volatile, self-obsessed,

420
00:26:33,879 --> 00:26:35,123
和他人难以相处
don't play well with others.

421
00:26:35,422 --> 00:26:36,417
这个我深有感触
That I did know.

422
00:26:36,548 --> 00:26:38,172
现在没空管性格了
This isn't about personality profiles anymore.

423
00:26:38,341 --> 00:26:40,666
无所谓了，宝芝小姐，可以过来下吗？
Whatever. Ms. Potts, got a second?

424
00:26:40,886 --> 00:26:41,880
稍等
Half a mo.

425
00:26:47,184 --> 00:26:49,508
我还以为我们能共度良宵哪
You know, I thought we were having a moment.

426
00:26:49,728 --> 00:26:51,304
我正在享受那12%的良宵
I was having 12% of a moment.

427
00:26:52,522 --> 00:26:54,977
事态看来挺严重的，费尔惊魂未定
This seems serious. Phil's pretty shaken.

428
00:26:55,192 --> 00:26:57,148
你知道那是…你怎么叫他费尔？
How would you know if it's... Why is he "Phil"?

429
00:26:57,360 --> 00:26:59,103
这都是些什么？
What is all this?

430
00:26:59,321 --> 00:27:00,862
这些是
This is

431
00:27:01,573 --> 00:27:02,568
看吧
this.

432
00:27:02,539 --> 00:27:04,457


433
00:27:09,915 --> 00:27:11,289
我今晚就飞华盛顿
I'm going to take the jet to DC tonight.

434
00:27:11,416 --> 00:27:12,446
明天吧
Tomorrow.

435
00:27:12,584 --> 00:27:14,872
你资料要看，还不少呢
You have homework. You have a lot of homework.

436
00:27:15,087 --> 00:27:16,793
要是我不看呢？
Well, what if I didn't?

437
00:27:17,422 --> 00:27:18,797
- 你不看？- 是啊
- If you didn't? - Yeah.

438
00:27:19,007 --> 00:27:21,165
你是说你已经看完了？
You mean when you've finished?

439
00:27:22,260 --> 00:27:25,545
那好吧
Well, then...

440
00:27:30,769 --> 00:27:32,048
就这么定了，一路顺风
Square deal. Fly safe.

441
00:27:36,273 --> 00:27:37,387
好好干
Work hard.

442
00:27:40,277 --> 00:27:42,020
去拉瓜迪亚机场顺路吗？
So, any chance you're driving by LaGuardia?

443
00:27:42,238 --> 00:27:44,988
- 我载你去吧 - 太棒了
- I can drop you. - Fantastic.

444
00:27:45,116 --> 00:27:46,110
说说那个大提琴手吧
I want to hear

445
00:27:46,242 --> 00:27:47,901
你们还有戏吗？
about the cellist. Is that still a thing?

446
00:27:48,119 --> 00:27:49,232
她搬回波特兰了
She moved back to Portland.

447
00:27:49,453 --> 00:27:52,572
真的吗？
What? BOO!

448
00:28:00,631 --> 00:28:03,038
我们距基地还有40分钟航程，长官
We're about 40 minutes out from home base, sir.

449
00:28:06,762 --> 00:28:10,426
班纳博士想复制我曾注射的血清吗？
So, this Dr. Banner was trying to replicate the serum they used on me?

450
00:28:10,641 --> 00:28:12,182
很多人都想
A lot of people were.

451
00:28:12,393 --> 00:28:14,016
你是世界上第一个超级英雄
You were the world's first superhero.

452
00:28:14,728 --> 00:28:17,432
班纳认为破解艾斯金的原始配方的关键
Banner thought gamma radiation might hold the key to unlocking

453
00:28:17,606 --> 00:28:18,934
就在于伽玛射线
Erskine's original formula.

454
00:28:19,984 --> 00:28:21,358
只可惜事与愿违，不是吗？
Didn't really go his way, did it?

455
00:28:21,777 --> 00:28:23,235
差不多吧
Not so much.

456
00:28:23,446 --> 00:28:26,280
不过他不变身的时候就像史蒂芬·霍金一样
When he's not that thing, though, the guy's like a Stephen Hawking.

457
00:28:28,325 --> 00:28:30,862
我是指智力方面
He's like a smart person.

458
00:28:32,997 --> 00:28:34,110
说实话
I gotta say,

459
00:28:34,457 --> 00:28:36,863
十分荣幸能与你正式会面
it's an honour to meet you officially.

460
00:28:37,626 --> 00:28:39,120
我是，我以前也算见过你
I've sort of met you. I mean,

461
00:28:39,295 --> 00:28:41,085
是你还在沉睡的时候
I watched you while you were sleeping.

462
00:28:42,923 --> 00:28:45,129
你被发现冰封不醒时
I mean, I was present

463
00:28:45,342 --> 00:28:48,627
我就在场
while you were unconscious from the ice.

464
00:28:48,846 --> 00:28:51,134
你能加入我们
You know, it's really just a huge honour

465
00:28:51,265 --> 00:28:53,221
实在是太荣幸了
to have you on board this...

466
00:28:53,601 --> 00:28:55,473
希望我可以胜任吧
I hope I'm the man for the job.

467
00:28:55,686 --> 00:28:58,556
你当然可以，绝对的
Oh, you are. Absolutely.

468
00:28:58,773 --> 00:29:01,642
我们对你的战斗服做了些改动
We made some modifications to the uniform.

469
00:29:01,859 --> 00:29:03,352
还采纳了些我的意见
I had a little design input.

470
00:29:03,569 --> 00:29:04,813
战斗服？
The uniform?

471
00:29:05,029 --> 00:29:07,519
那些星条旗图案…
Aren't the stars and stripes a little

472
00:29:08,699 --> 00:29:10,027
是不是有些过时？
old-fashioned?

473
00:29:10,868 --> 00:29:13,025
鉴于目前局势
With everything that's happening

474
00:29:13,245 --> 00:29:14,869
和未来可能发生的事情
and the things that are about to come to light,

475
00:29:15,748 --> 00:29:19,198
人们可能需要一些过去的美国精神
people might just need a little old-fashioned.

476
00:29:37,569 --> 00:29:39,154


477
00:29:51,742 --> 00:29:54,695
智塔利人已经等不及了
The Chitauri grow restless.

478
00:29:54,912 --> 00:29:56,619
让他们做好战备吧
Let them gird themselves.

479
00:29:56,747 --> 00:29:58,538
我将引领他们打一场光荣的战役
I will lead them in the glorious battle.

480
00:29:58,749 --> 00:29:59,911
战役？
Battle?

481
00:30:00,751 --> 00:30:03,835
对付那些弱小的地球人？
Against the meagre might of Earth?

482
00:30:04,046 --> 00:30:06,880
一场光荣的闪电战
Glorious, not lengthy.

483
00:30:07,091 --> 00:30:10,874
只要你的大军如你所言般强大
If your force is as formidable as you claim.

484
00:30:11,095 --> 00:30:13,585
你竟然质疑我们？
You question us?

485
00:30:13,806 --> 00:30:15,928
你质疑的人
You question him,

486
00:30:16,099 --> 00:30:18,553
正是在你战败且遭受流放时
he who put the sceptre in your hand?

487
00:30:18,768 --> 00:30:21,685
授予你权杖
Who gave you ancient knowledge and new purpose

488
00:30:21,896 --> 00:30:24,766
并给予你远古知识与新的目标的人
when you were cast out, defeated?

489
00:30:24,983 --> 00:30:26,855
我是国王
I was a king!

490
00:30:27,068 --> 00:30:29,274
亚斯加特的法定国王
The rightful king of Asgard,

491
00:30:29,779 --> 00:30:30,774
可惜遭人背叛
betrayed.

492
00:30:31,448 --> 00:30:34,068
你鼠目寸光
Your ambition is little

493
00:30:34,284 --> 00:30:37,034
满是幼稚之想
and born of childish need.

494
00:30:37,245 --> 00:30:39,237
我们放眼地球之外
We look beyond the Earth

495
00:30:39,456 --> 00:30:42,409
那些即将被宇宙立方开启的无垠星空
to the greater worlds the Tesseract will unveil.

496
00:30:42,876 --> 00:30:44,285
可惜宇宙立方还在我手上
You don't have the Tesseract yet.

497
00:30:47,088 --> 00:30:48,083
我可没有威胁你
I don't threaten.

498
00:30:49,632 --> 00:30:52,205
但只要传送门没有打开
But until I open the doors,

499
00:30:52,427 --> 00:30:56,044
你的大军没有归于我的麾下
until your force is mine to command,

500
00:30:56,806 --> 00:30:58,597
你的一切都只是空谈
you are but words.

501
00:30:58,808 --> 00:31:02,757
你会得到想要的战争的，亚斯加特人
You will have your war, Asgardian.

502
00:31:04,564 --> 00:31:06,556
如果你失败了
If you fail,

503
00:31:07,567 --> 00:31:11,943
宇宙立方落入他人之手
if the Tesseract is kept from us,

504
00:31:12,155 --> 00:31:16,531
那将没有任何国家，任何星球
there will be no realm, no barren moon,

505
00:31:16,743 --> 00:31:20,027
哪怕一道裂隙供你躲藏
no crevice where he cannot find you.

506
00:31:21,623 --> 00:31:24,373
你知道苦痛的滋味吗？
You think you know pain?

507
00:31:24,584 --> 00:31:30,253
他会让你体验真正的痛不欲生
He will make you long for something sweet as pain.

508
00:31:30,265 --> 00:31:31,641


509
00:31:59,452 --> 00:32:00,482
把美国队长的装备卸载下来
Stow the captain's gear.

510
00:32:00,620 --> 00:32:01,615
遵命，长官
Yes, sir.

511
00:32:03,164 --> 00:32:06,283
罗曼诺夫探员，这位是罗杰斯队长
Agent Romanoff, Captain Rogers.

512
00:32:06,501 --> 00:32:07,780
- 你好，女士 - 你好
- Ma'am. - Hi.

513
00:32:07,961 --> 00:32:08,956
他们在舰桥等着你
They need you on the bridge.

514
00:32:09,087 --> 00:32:10,580
他们开始面部识别追踪了
They're starting the face-trace.

515
00:32:10,797 --> 00:32:11,875
回见
See you there.

516
00:32:13,633 --> 00:32:17,760
你在冰中被发现可轰动一时呢
It was quite the buzz around here, finding you in the ice.

517
00:32:18,054 --> 00:32:20,627
我以为古逊会乐晕了呢
I thought Coulson was gonna swoon.

518
00:32:20,849 --> 00:32:23,718
他没让你在美国队长集换卡上签名？
Did he ask you to sign his Captain America trading cards yet?

519
00:32:23,935 --> 00:32:25,132
集换卡？
Trading cards?

520
00:32:25,353 --> 00:32:27,511
珍藏版的，他可引以为傲呢
They're vintage. He's very proud.

521
00:32:29,274 --> 00:32:30,553
班纳博士
Dr. Banner.

522
00:32:32,569 --> 00:32:33,848
你好啊
Yeah, hi.

523
00:32:34,404 --> 00:32:35,601
我听说你会过来
They told me you would be coming.

524
00:32:35,822 --> 00:32:37,101
他们说你能找到那立方
Word is, you can find the Cube.

525
00:32:38,158 --> 00:32:40,030
就说了这些？
Is that the only word on me?

526
00:32:40,452 --> 00:32:41,613
我就关心这些
Only word I care about.

527
00:32:44,205 --> 00:32:46,790
这些一定让你倍感陌生吧
It must be strange for you, all of this.

528
00:32:47,500 --> 00:32:50,169
其实，我倒觉得似曾相识
Well, this is actually kind of familiar.

529
00:32:50,378 --> 00:32:52,951
先生们，你们最好赶紧进去
Gentlemen, you might want to step inside in a minute.

530
00:32:53,173 --> 00:32:55,923
这儿马上就难以呼吸了
It's going to get a little hard to breathe.

531
00:32:57,176 --> 00:32:58,717
空勤人员，请清空甲板
Flight crew, secure the deck.

532
00:33:03,223 --> 00:33:04,800
这是潜艇吗？
Is this a submarine?

533
00:33:05,350 --> 00:33:06,345
真的？
Really?

534
00:33:06,477 --> 00:33:10,224
想把我关在水下加压的金属管子里？
They want me in a submerged, pressurised, metal container?

535
00:33:28,049 --> 00:33:30,593


536
00:33:36,632 --> 00:33:39,003
不，好像更糟
No, no, this is much worse.

537
00:33:57,203 --> 00:33:59,414


538
00:34:08,831 --> 00:34:11,534
悬停能量检查完毕，供给稳定
Hover power check complete. Position cyclic.

539
00:34:11,750 --> 00:34:14,157
动力增至8%
Increase collective to 8.0%.

540
00:34:19,258 --> 00:34:21,545
准备全速启航
Preparing for maximum performance takeoff.

541
00:34:21,677 --> 00:34:23,170
输出功率调至最高
Increase output to capacity.

542
00:34:23,345 --> 00:34:25,467
动力性能已达上限
Power plant performing at capacity.

543
00:34:25,681 --> 00:34:27,139
准备完毕
We are clear.

544
00:34:27,349 --> 00:34:28,842
全部引擎运转正常
All engines operating.

545
00:34:29,059 --> 00:34:33,685
神盾局193.6号应急规程已启动
S.H.I.E.L.D. Emergency Protocol 193.6 in effect.

546
00:34:33,939 --> 00:34:36,476
- 已到达预定高度，长官 - 很好
- We are at level, sir. - Good.

547
00:34:36,859 --> 00:34:37,853
我们消失吧
Let's vanish.

548
00:34:38,068 --> 00:34:40,475
开启光线反射板
Engage retro-reflection panels.

549
00:34:56,253 --> 00:34:57,415
光线反射板开启完毕
Reflection panels engaged.

550
00:34:58,046 --> 00:34:59,421
先生们
Gentlemen.

551
00:35:11,769 --> 00:35:12,882
感谢你的到来，博士
Doctor, thank you for coming.

552
00:35:14,897 --> 00:35:16,769
多谢你的善意邀请
Thanks for asking nicely.

553
00:35:16,982 --> 00:35:19,602
那我要在这呆多久？
So, how long am I staying?

554
00:35:19,818 --> 00:35:21,609
等我们拿到宇宙立方
Once we get our hands on the Tesseract,

555
00:35:21,737 --> 00:35:22,934
你就可以走了
you're in the wind.

556
00:35:23,071 --> 00:35:24,897
你那边有何进展？
Where are you with that?

557
00:35:25,115 --> 00:35:26,858
我们在扫描地球上每一个
We're sweeping every wirelessly accessible

558
00:35:26,992 --> 00:35:27,987
连接到无线网络的摄像头
camera on the planet.

559
00:35:28,577 --> 00:35:30,367
手机，笔记本电脑…
Cell phones, laptops...

560
00:35:30,913 --> 00:35:34,197
只要它连上了卫星，就成了我们的眼线
If it's connected to a satellite, it's eyes and ears for us.

561
00:35:34,416 --> 00:35:35,660
这样还是无法及时找到他们
That's still not gonna find them in time.

562
00:35:35,876 --> 00:35:36,871
你得缩小搜寻范围
You have to narrow your field.

563
00:35:37,086 --> 00:35:39,042
你们有多少光谱仪可用？
How many spectrometers do you have access to?

564
00:35:39,253 --> 00:35:40,877
- 你要多少？ - 通知所有可以联系上的实验室
- How many are there? - Call every lab you know.

565
00:35:41,089 --> 00:35:42,795
让他们把光谱仪放在房顶
Tell them to put the spectrometers on the roof

566
00:35:42,924 --> 00:35:44,381
调整成接收伽玛射线的状态
and calibrate them for gamma rays.

567
00:35:44,592 --> 00:35:47,794
我会草拟一个聚类识别的追踪算法
I'll rough out a tracking algorithm, basic cluster recognition.

568
00:35:48,096 --> 00:35:50,502
最少能排除一些区域
At least we could rule out a few places.

569
00:35:50,765 --> 00:35:52,555
能给我找个干活的地方吗？
Do you have somewhere for me to work?

570
00:35:52,809 --> 00:35:53,922
罗曼诺夫探员
Agent Romanoff,

571
00:35:54,102 --> 00:35:56,342
能把班纳博士带到他的实验室去吗？
could you show Dr. Banner to his laboratory, please?

572
00:35:57,480 --> 00:35:59,721
