It's very hard to get hold of.

581
00:36:16,916 --> 00:36:18,457
如果神盾局知道你需要它，就更难了
Especially if S.H.I.E.L.D. knows you need it.

582
00:36:18,668 --> 00:36:20,042
这我就不知道了
