These guys come from legend. They're basically gods.

691
00:44:37,330 --> 00:44:38,610
世上只有上帝一个神，女士
There's only one God, ma'am.

692
00:44:38,748 --> 00:44:41,119
而且他才不会打扮成那样
And I'm pretty sure he doesn't dress like that.

693
00:44:52,191 --> 00:44:53,734


694
00:44:54,818 --> 00:44:56,236


695
00:44:56,599 --> 00:44:57,974
