那当然
Well, yes.

725
00:46:14,010 --> 00:46:16,465
那你就没懂得统治的真谛，弟弟
Then you miss the truth of ruling, brother.

726
00:46:17,305 --> 00:46:18,679
王位并不适合你
A throne would suit you ill.

727
00:46:23,895 --> 00:46:26,646
我见过许多你未知的世界
I've seen worlds you've never known about!

728
00:46:26,856 --> 00:46:31,019
奥丁逊，在流放途中，我已成长
I have grown, Odinson, in my exile.

729
00:46:31,401 --> 00:46:33,358
我见识了宇宙立方的真正力量
I have seen the true power of the Tesseract,

730
00:46:33,487 --> 00:46:34,565
等我拥有了它…
and when I wield it...

731
00:46:34,780 --> 00:46:36,522
谁向你展示了它的力量？
Who showed you this power?

732
00:46:37,699 --> 00:46:39,027
是谁在背后操纵着你这个国王迷？
Who controls the would-be king?

733
00:46:39,243 --> 00:46:41,033
- 我就是国王！- 别妄想了！
- I am a king! - Not here!

734
00:46:41,245 --> 00:46:42,524
交出宇宙立方！
You give up the Tesseract!

735
00:46:42,663 --> 00:46:45,200
放下痴心妄想！
You give up this poisonous dream!

736
00:46:47,918 --> 00:46:49,292
跟我回家
You come home.

737
00:46:54,258 --> 00:46:55,371
不在我手上
I don't have it.

738
00:46:57,469 --> 00:46:59,260
你需要立方来带我回去
You need the Cube to bring me home.

739
00:46:59,388 --> 00:47:01,712
