先跟你说清楚了
In case it's unclear,

784
00:51:08,261 --> 00:51:10,051
如果你想逃跑
if you try to escape,

785
00:51:11,139 --> 00:51:13,426
哪怕轻轻挠那玻璃一下
if you so much as scratch that glass,

786
00:51:15,449 --> 00:51:17,325


787
00:51:23,025 --> 00:51:26,974
你就会随着这监牢从万米高空坠落
it's 30,000 feet straight down in a steel trap.

788
00:51:27,530 --> 00:51:29,652
懂了吗？
You get how that works?

789
00:51:31,701 --> 00:51:34,321
你是蚂蚁，我是靴子
Ant, boot.

790
00:51:34,426 --> 00:51:36,511


791
00:51:37,665 --> 00:51:39,408
这笼子可真不错
It's an impressive cage.

792
00:51:40,334 --> 00:51:42,955
不过，不是为我建造的吧
Not built, I think, for me.

793
00:51:43,337 --> 00:51:45,744
它是为个比你强大得多的东西建的
Built for something a lot stronger than you.

794
00:51:45,965 --> 00:51:47,838
我有所耳闻
Oh, I've heard.

795
00:51:48,843 --> 00:51:50,005
一头愚蠢的野兽
A mindless beast.

796
00:51:51,012 --> 00:51:52,635
还假装自己是普通人
Makes play he's still a man.

797
00:51:53,722 --> 00:51:55,963
你该有多绝望
How desperate are you,

798
00:51:56,183 --> 00:51:59,266
才会找来这种怪胎作援兵？
that you call on such lost creatures to defend you?

799
00:51:59,478 --> 00:52:01,802
我有多绝望？
How desperate am I?

800
00:52:02,022 --> 00:52:03,812
你以战争威胁我们的世界
You threaten my world with war.

801
00:52:04,024 --> 00:52:06,146
你窃取自己无法掌控的能量
You steal a force you can't hope to control.

802
00:52:06,359 --> 00:52:10,142
你嘴边挂着安宁，却以挥舞手中屠刀为乐
You talk about peace, and you kill because it's fun.

803
00:52:10,363 --> 00:52:13,363
你逼我孤注一掷
You have made me very desperate.

804
00:52:13,575 --> 00:52:15,483
你会为你的所作所为后悔的
You might not be glad that you did.

805
00:52:15,884 --> 00:52:17,177
噢
Ooh.

806
00:52:18,747 --> 00:52:22,031
功亏一篑让你无比痛苦吧
It burns you to have come so close.

807
00:52:23,502 --> 00:52:26,205
获取宇宙立方，拥有其中能量
To have the Tesseract, to have power,

808
00:52:27,005 --> 00:52:29,210
无尽的能量
unlimited power.

809
00:52:29,424 --> 00:52:31,380
用来干什么？
And for what?

810
00:52:33,762 --> 00:52:36,845
点起照亮人类前路的明灯
A warm light for all mankind to share.

811
00:52:37,099 --> 00:52:40,348
然后认识到真正力量的本来面目
And then to be reminded what real power is.

812
00:52:44,439 --> 00:52:48,732
如果真正力量想要看杂志解闷，记得跟我说
Well, let me know if "real power" wants a magazine or something.

813
00:52:57,077 --> 00:52:58,535
你都看他看入迷了吧
He really grows on you, doesn't he?

814
00:52:58,745 --> 00:53:00,653
洛基是在拖延时间
Loki's gonna drag this out.

815
00:53:00,872 --> 00:53:04,323
托尔，他到底想干什么？
So, Thor, what's his play?

816
00:53:04,543 --> 00:53:07,080
他拥有一支智塔利大军
He has an army called the Chitauri.

817
00:53:07,295 --> 00:53:10,212
他们并非来自亚斯加特或任何已知的世界
They're not of Asgard, nor any world known.

818
00:53:10,632 --> 00:53:12,707
洛基想带领他们攻打地球
He means to lead them against your people.

819
00:53:12,926 --> 00:53:14,503
他们将助洛基夺取地球
They will win him the Earth,

820
00:53:14,636 --> 00:53:16,426
而我想洛基会将宇宙立方交给他们
in return, I suspect, for the Tesseract.

821
00:53:16,638 --> 00:53:18,380
来自外太空的
An army

822
00:53:18,598 --> 00:53:20,257
大军
from outer space.

823
00:53:20,475 --> 00:53:22,882
那么他正在建立另一个传送门
So, he's building another portal.

824
00:53:23,103 --> 00:53:24,430
这就是他带走艾力·绍韦的原因
That's what he needs Erik Selvig for.

825
00:53:24,563 --> 00:53:25,557
绍韦？
Selvig?

826
00:53:25,730 --> 00:53:28,055
- 他是位天体物理学家 - 我的朋友
- He's an astrophysicist. - He's a friend.

827
00:53:28,275 --> 00:53:30,397
洛基用某种魔法控制了他
Loki has him under some kind of spell,

828
00:53:30,569 --> 00:53:32,062
还有我们的一位探员
along with one of ours.

829
00:53:32,279 --> 00:53:33,855
洛基为何如此轻易的束手就擒
I want to know why Loki let us take him.

830
00:53:33,989 --> 00:53:35,268
他在这无法领导任何大军
He's not leading an army from here.

831
00:53:35,490 --> 00:53:37,197
我觉得不应该把注意力集中在洛基身上
I don't think we should be focusing on Loki.

832
00:53:37,409 --> 00:53:39,199
他的想法难以捉摸
That guy's brain is a bag full of cats.

833
00:53:39,327 --> 00:53:40,607
可以说就是个疯子
You could smell crazy on him.

834
00:53:40,829 --> 00:53:42,571
说话注意点
Have care how you speak.

835
00:53:43,123 --> 00:53:45,328
尽管洛基蛮不讲理，但他还是亚斯加特人
Loki is beyond reason, but he is of Asgard.

836
00:53:45,751 --> 00:53:46,829
也是我的弟弟
And he is my brother.

837
00:53:47,043 --> 00:53:48,916
他在两天内杀了80个人
He killed 80 people in two days.

838
00:53:49,796 --> 00:53:50,791
不是亲弟弟
He's adopted.

839
00:53:50,964 --> 00:53:53,252
让我们往机械上想想吧
I think it's about the mechanics.

840
00:53:53,467 --> 00:53:55,423
铱，他们要铱干什么？
Iridium... What do they need the iridium for?

841
00:53:55,635 --> 00:53:56,630
铱是一种稳定剂
It's a stabilising agent.

842
00:53:56,803 --> 00:53:58,083
我是说，随便那个周末
I'm just saying, pick a weekend.

843
00:53:58,221 --> 00:53:59,762
我开飞机载你去波特兰
I'll fly you to Portland.

844
00:53:59,973 --> 00:54:01,514
多培养一下情感
Keep love alive.

845
00:54:01,725 --> 00:54:05,594
这样传送门就不会像神盾局的那个一样自我坍塌了
It means the portal won't collapse on itself like it did at S.H.I.E.L.D.

846
00:54:05,812 --> 00:54:09,097
不打不相识，你那一下真狠
No hard feelings, Point Break. You've got a mean swing.

847
00:54:09,316 --> 00:54:11,557
同时铱还可以让洛基根据需要
Also, it means the portal can open as wide

848
00:54:11,777 --> 00:54:14,183
把传送门开得更大，持续时间更长
and stay open as long, as Loki wants.

849
00:54:14,905 --> 00:54:17,110
升起后桅，全速启航
Raise the mizzenmast. Jib the topsails.

850
00:54:18,825 --> 00:54:20,022
那人在玩「小蜜蜂」
That man is playing Galaga.

851
00:54:21,078 --> 00:54:24,446
他自以为别人看不到，但被我发现了
He thought we wouldn't notice, but we did.

852
00:54:26,416 --> 00:54:27,791
霍利的视线如何兼顾两侧？
How does Fury even see these?

853
00:54:27,959 --> 00:54:28,954
他会转身
He turns.

854
00:54:29,252 --> 00:54:30,876
那多累啊
Sounds exhausting.

855
00:54:31,963 --> 00:54:33,125
剩余的原材料
The rest of the raw materials,

856
00:54:33,340 --> 00:54:36,126
巴顿探员都能轻松得到
Agent Barton can get his hands on pretty easily.

857
00:54:36,342 --> 00:54:37,716
现在他只需要一个部件
The only major component he still needs

858
00:54:37,927 --> 00:54:41,425
高能量密度的动力源
is a power source of high-energy density.

859
00:54:41,639 --> 00:54:44,888
来启动立方
Something to kick-start the Cube.

860
00:54:45,101 --> 00:54:48,054
你什么时候变成热核天体物理学家了？
When did you become an expert in thermonuclear astrophysics?

861
00:54:48,270 --> 00:54:49,265
昨天晚上
Last night.

862
00:54:49,772 --> 00:54:52,974
看看任务资料，绍韦的笔记和精选的理论论文
The packet, Selvig's notes, the extraction theory papers.

863
00:54:53,192 --> 00:54:54,187
难道只有我看了？
Am I the only one who did the reading?

864
00:54:54,360 --> 00:54:57,146
洛基需要某种特定的能源吗？
Does Loki need any particular kind of power source?

865
00:54:57,363 --> 00:55:00,067
他得把立方加热到1.2亿开氏度
He would have to heat the Cube to 120-million Kelvin

866
00:55:00,282 --> 00:55:01,740
以突破库仑势垒
just to break through the Coulomb barrier.

867
00:55:01,951 --> 00:55:04,156
除非绍韦找到
Unless Selvig has figured out how to stabilise

868
00:55:04,370 --> 00:55:05,483
稳定量子隧道效应的办法
the quantum tunneling effect.

869
00:55:05,704 --> 00:55:06,699
如果他真找到了
Well, if he could do that,

870
00:55:06,872 --> 00:55:09,327
就可以用地球上任一个反应堆完成重离子聚变
he could achieve heavy ion fusion at any reactor on the planet.

871
00:55:09,542 --> 00:55:11,948
终于有会说人话的了
Finally, someone who speaks English.

872
00:55:12,169 --> 00:55:14,125
是那么回事吗？
Is that what just happened?

873
00:55:14,338 --> 00:55:16,330
很高兴见到你，班纳博士
It's good to meet you, Dr. Banner.

874
00:55:16,549 --> 00:55:19,584
你在反电子冲撞领域中的成就无人能及
Your work on antielectron collisions is unparalleled.

875
00:55:19,802 --> 00:55:21,592
我也是你失控时变成的
And I'm a huge fan of the way you lose control

876
00:55:21,804 --> 00:55:23,842
那个绿色大怪兽的铁杆粉丝
and turn into an enormous green rage-monster.

877
00:55:25,391 --> 00:55:26,421
谢谢
Thanks.

878
00:55:26,642 --> 00:55:29,132
班纳博士只为追寻立方而来
Dr. Banner is only here to track the Cube.

879
00:55:29,353 --> 00:55:30,633
我希望你可以助他一臂之力
I was hoping you might join him.

880
00:55:30,855 --> 00:55:32,016
从他的权杖开始看吧
I would start with that stick of his.

881
00:55:32,148 --> 00:55:33,178
它也许有魔力
It may be magical,

882
00:55:33,315 --> 00:55:34,595
但用法和海德拉的武器挺像的
but it works an awful lot like a HYDRA weapon.

883
00:55:34,734 --> 00:55:37,769
我不大清楚，但它由立方所驱动
I don't know about that, but it is powered by the Cube.

884
00:55:38,070 --> 00:55:39,813
我想知道洛基怎么用它
And I would like to know how Loki used it

885
00:55:40,030 --> 00:55:41,607
把我见过的最机警的两个人
to turn two of the sharpest men I know

886
00:55:41,741 --> 00:55:43,531
变成他的跟班飞猴
into his personal flying monkeys.

887
00:55:43,909 --> 00:55:45,451
猴子？你在说什么
Monkeys? I do not understand.

888
00:55:45,578 --> 00:55:46,572
绿野仙踪，我知道
I do.

889
00:55:49,582 --> 00:55:51,454
我知道这典故
I understood that reference.

890
00:55:52,376 --> 00:55:53,704
我们开始吧，博士？
Shall we play, Doctor?

891
00:55:53,919 --> 00:55:55,626
这边请，先生
This way, sir.

892
00:56:09,602 --> 00:56:11,178
伽玛读数和绍韦报告上
The gamma readings are definitely consistent

893
00:56:11,395 --> 00:56:13,387
宇宙立方的读数完全一致
with Selvig's reports of the Tesseract.

894
00:56:13,773 --> 00:56:15,396
但处理起来要花好几周时间
But it's going to take weeks to process.

895
00:56:15,608 --> 00:56:16,805
如果可以绕过他们的主机
If we bypass their mainframe

896
00:56:16,942 --> 00:56:18,222
连接到主群集
and direct route to the Homer cluster,

897
00:56:18,444 --> 00:56:21,527
我们可以做到每秒600兆次浮点运算
we can clock this at around 600 teraflops.

898
00:56:22,698 --> 00:56:24,654
可惜我只带了牙刷
All I packed was a toothbrush.

899
00:56:25,743 --> 00:56:27,319
有空来史塔大厦玩玩
You know, you should come by Stark Tower sometime.

900
00:56:27,536 --> 00:56:29,575
顶10层用作科研
Top ten floors, all R&D.

901
00:56:29,914 --> 00:56:31,371
包你喜欢
You'd love it. It's Candy Land.

902
00:56:31,582 --> 00:56:34,072
谢了，上次我在纽约
Thanks, but the last time I was in New York,

903
00:56:34,293 --> 00:56:36,830
差点炸了哈莱姆区
I kind of broke Harlem.

904
00:56:37,046 --> 00:56:38,872
我保证这次你会毫无压力
Well, I promise a stress-free environment.

905
00:56:39,090 --> 00:56:40,880
毫不紧张，绝无意外
No tension, no surprises.

906
00:56:40,899 --> 00:56:42,233
- Ow!

907
00:56:42,317 --> 00:56:43,735
Hey! - Nothing?

908
00:56:44,095 --> 00:56:45,089
你疯了？
Are you nuts?

909
00:56:45,221 --> 00:56:46,215
天晓得
Jury's out.

910
00:56:46,347 --> 00:56:47,460
自制力不错啊
You really have got a lid on it, haven't you?

911
00:56:47,598 --> 00:56:48,593
有何秘诀？
What's your secret?

912
00:56:48,724 --> 00:56:50,182
玩爵士乐还是磕药？
Mellow jazz, bongo drums huge bag of weed?

913
00:56:50,351 --> 00:56:51,464
你很爱开玩笑吗？
Is everything a joke to you?

914
00:56:51,769 --> 00:56:52,764
好玩嘛
Funny things are.

915
00:56:52,895 --> 00:56:54,637
这会令大家身陷险境
Threatening the safety of everyone on this ship

916
00:56:54,772 --> 00:56:56,016
何来好玩
isn't funny.

917
00:56:56,148 --> 00:56:57,143
对不起，博士
No offence, Doc.

918
00:56:57,274 --> 00:56:58,768
没关系，若我连这小刺激都适应不了
It's all right, I wouldn't have come aboard

919
00:56:58,901 --> 00:57:01,735
就不会登船了
if I couldn't handle pointy things.

920
00:57:01,862 --> 00:57:04,435
大块头，你太谨慎了，放松点
You're tip-toeing, big man. You need to strut.

921
00:57:04,573 --> 00:57:06,232
而你需要专注解决问题，史塔先生
And you need to focus on the problem, Mr. Stark.

922
00:57:06,367 --> 00:57:07,860
难道我没有做事吗？
Do you think I'm not?

923
00:57:07,993 --> 00:57:10,780
为何霍利现在才召集我们？
Why did Fury call us in? Why now? Why not before?

924
00:57:10,913 --> 00:57:12,655
有何内幕？
What isn't he telling us?

925
00:57:12,790 --> 00:57:14,532
消除所有疑惑，我才能做事
I can't do the equation unless I have all the variables.

926
00:57:15,167 --> 00:57:16,411
你指霍利有所隐瞒？
You think Fury's hiding something?

927
00:57:16,544 --> 00:57:19,709
毕竟他可是特务中的佼佼者
He's a spy. Captain, he's "the" spy.

928
00:57:19,838 --> 00:57:21,580
深不可测
His secrets have secrets.

929
00:57:21,714 --> 00:57:23,208
他也有同感吧？
It's bugging him, too. Isn't it?

930
00:57:23,233 --> 00:57:24,234
Uh...

931
00:57:25,802 --> 00:57:27,592
我只想完成我在这里的工作
I just want to finish my work here, and...

932
00:57:27,720 --> 00:57:28,715
博士?
Doctor?

933
00:57:34,144 --> 00:57:36,515
点起照亮人类前程的明灯
"A warm light for all mankind."

934
00:57:36,646 --> 00:57:38,721
提及宇宙立方时，洛基这样对霍利说道
Loki's jab at Fury about the Cube.

935
00:57:38,857 --> 00:57:40,314
我听见了
I heard it.

936
00:57:40,442 --> 00:57:42,729
是说给你听的
I think that was meant for you.

937
00:57:43,445 --> 00:57:46,398
即使巴顿没跟洛基提过史塔大厦
Even if Barton didn't tell Loki about the tower,

938
00:57:46,531 --> 00:57:47,609
他也可以由新闻得知
it was still all over the news.

939
00:57:47,741 --> 00:57:49,816
史塔大厦？高耸又奇丑…
The Stark Tower? That big, ugly

940
00:57:51,161 --> 00:57:52,405
的纽约建筑大厦？
building in New York?

941
00:57:52,537 --> 00:57:56,237
由弦反应炉供能，能源可自生
It's powered by an arc reactor, a self-sustaining energy source.

942
00:57:56,374 --> 00:57:58,781
大厦能自给自足一年吗？
That building will run itself for, what, a year?

943
00:57:58,918 --> 00:58:00,744
只是个试点
It's just the prototype.

944
00:58:00,879 --> 00:58:02,835
我可是目前洁净能源的先驱者
I'm kind of the only name in clean energy right now.

945
00:58:03,256 --> 00:58:04,666
这就是他的目的
That's what he's getting at.

946
00:58:04,799 --> 00:58:07,372
为何神盾局没招揽他加入宇宙立方计划？
So, why didn't S.H.I.E.L.D. bring him in on the Tesseract project?

947
00:58:07,510 --> 00:58:10,715
当初为何他们会涉足能源产业？
What are they doing in the energy business in the first place?

948
00:58:10,847 --> 00:58:13,800
一旦我获悉所有神盾局的机密
I should probably look into that once my decryption program

949
00:58:13,933 --> 00:58:16,091
我会着手调查此事
finishes breaking into all of S.H.I.E.L.D.'s secure files.

950
00:58:16,227 --> 00:58:17,222
对不起，你说…
I'm sorry. Did you say...

951
00:58:17,353 --> 00:58:19,345
自我上船来，佐维斯就一直运行破解程式
Jarvis has been running it since I hit the bridge.

952
00:58:19,481 --> 00:58:21,057
几小时后，我就可以得知
In a few hours, I'll know every dirty secret

953
00:58:21,191 --> 00:58:22,352
神盾局的隐藏机密
S.H.I.E.L.D. has ever tried to hide.

954
00:58:22,484 --> 00:58:23,478
吃蓝莓吗?
Blueberry?

955
00:58:23,610 --> 00:58:25,482
你仍为没被招揽而百思不解？
Yet you're confused about why they didn't want you around.

956
00:58:25,612 --> 00:58:28,446
情报机构竟然害怕聪明人？
An intelligence organisation that fears intelligence?

957
00:58:28,573 --> 00:58:30,150
真没劲
Historically, not awesome.

958
00:58:30,283 --> 00:58:32,571
洛基想挑拨离间
I think Loki's trying to wind us up.

959
00:58:32,702 --> 00:58:34,279
洛基肯定意图发动战争
This is a man who means to start a war

960
00:58:34,412 --> 00:58:35,953
继续这样下去，岂不正中他下怀
and if we don't stay focused, he'll succeed.

961
00:58:37,248 --> 00:58:39,703
既然有命在身，就要服从
We have orders. We should follow them.

962
00:58:40,210 --> 00:58:42,201
我可不喜欢臣服于他人
Following's not really my style.

963
00:58:43,421 --> 00:58:45,792
你想出风头吧？
And you're all about style, aren't you?

964
00:58:45,924 --> 00:58:46,954
在座各位
Of the people in this room,

965
00:58:47,092 --> 00:58:48,668
当中有人着装奇异
which one is, A, wearing a spangly outfit,

966
00:58:48,802 --> 00:58:50,129
简直不成气候
and, B, not of use?

967
00:58:50,261 --> 00:58:54,590
斯蒂夫，你不觉得不自在吗？
Steve, tell me none of this smells a little funky to you.

968
00:58:57,310 --> 00:58:58,340
找立方吧
Just find the Cube.

969
00:59:00,747 --> 00:59:02,624


970
00:59:11,282 --> 00:59:13,191
他就是让我父亲赞不绝口的家伙？
That's the guy my dad never shut up about?

971
00:59:13,660 --> 00:59:16,446
他们应该再次冷藏他
I'm wondering if they shouldn't have kept him on ice.

972
00:59:15,803 --> 00:59:17,096
Huh.

973
00:59:17,288 --> 00:59:18,995
他很了解洛基
The guy's not wrong about Loki.

974
00:59:19,124 --> 00:59:20,866
他看事情比我们敏锐
He does have the jump on us.

975
00:59:21,000 --> 00:59:23,704
他就像导火索
What he's got is an Acme dynamite kit.

976
00:59:23,837 --> 00:59:25,662
迟早会搞砸一切
It's going to blow up in his face.

977
00:59:25,797 --> 00:59:28,085
到时我拭目以待
And I'm going to be there when it does.

978
00:59:28,383 --> 00:59:30,540
我就会由新闻得知过程
Yeah. I'll read all about it.

979
00:59:32,679 --> 00:59:33,958
不如你也着装加入我们
Uh-huh. Or you'll be suiting up with the rest of us.

980
00:59:33,821 --> 00:59:34,948


981
00:59:35,557 --> 00:59:39,138
你看，可我没有护甲
You see, I don't get a suit of armour.

982
00:59:39,269 --> 00:59:42,601
赤手空拳打战简直寻死
I'm exposed. Like a nerve.

983
00:59:42,730 --> 00:59:44,473
太糟糕了
It's a nightmare.

984
00:59:44,607 --> 00:59:47,394
每时每刻都有一堆炮弹碎片
I've got a cluster of shrapnel trying every second

985
00:59:47,527 --> 00:59:49,519
试图侵入我心脏
to crawl its way into my heart.

986
00:59:49,654 --> 00:59:51,693
这个保护了我
This stops it.

987
00:59:51,823 --> 00:59:54,147
这个小光环是我身体一部分了
This little circle of light, it's part of me now,

988
00:59:55,368 --> 00:59:57,027
不止是护甲
not just armour.

989
00:59:57,704 --> 01:00:00,158
是可怕的天赐
It's a terrible privilege.

990
01:00:00,497 --> 01:00:02,868
- 不过你可以控制它 - 我只是学会使用
- But you can control it. - Because I learned how.

991
01:00:03,000 --> 01:00:03,995
不能这样说
It's different.

992
01:00:04,334 --> 01:00:07,667
我听闻过你的事情
Hey, I read all about your accident.

993
01:00:07,796 --> 01:00:11,129
如此强的伽马射线早该杀死你
That much gamma exposure should have killed you.

994
01:00:11,258 --> 01:00:13,713
你意指绿巨人浩克
So you're saying that the Hulk...

995
01:00:15,179 --> 01:00:17,550
他救了我？
The other guy saved my life?

996
01:00:18,056 --> 01:00:19,170
说得好
That's nice.

997
01:00:20,058 --> 01:00:23,841
观点不错，可为什么救我？
It's a nice sentiment. Saved it for what?

998
01:00:25,147 --> 01:00:27,055
我们会知道的
I guess we'll find out.

999
01:00:28,776 --> 01:00:30,435
届时你就会闷闷不乐
You may not enjoy that.

1000
01:00:30,569 --> 01:00:32,525
说不定你会高兴起来
And you just might.

1001
01:00:35,180 --> 01:00:36,709
（机密仓库10-C）

1002
01:00:37,218 --> 01:00:39,262


1003
01:00:39,345 --> 01:00:40,805


1004
01:00:53,818 --> 01:00:55,570


1005
01:01:31,755 --> 01:01:33,130
洛基一带走博士
As soon as Loki took the doctor,

1006
01:01:33,257 --> 01:01:34,999
我们就把珍儿转移了
we moved Jane Foster.

1007
01:01:35,134 --> 01:01:37,505
挪威有个一流的天文台
They've got an excellent observatory in Tromsø.

1008
01:01:37,636 --> 01:01:41,170
珍儿昨天应邀过去做顾问
She was asked to consult there very suddenly yesterday.

1009
01:01:41,306 --> 01:01:45,089
酬劳不菲，有私人飞机，离这里很远
Handsome fee, private plane, very remote.

1010
01:01:45,978 --> 01:01:47,008
她会很安全
She'll be safe.

1011
01:01:47,146 --> 01:01:48,520
多谢
Thank you.

1012
01:01:50,315 --> 01:01:52,354
洛基带走艾力博士，并非巧合
It's no accident, Loki taking Erik Selvig.

1013
01:01:53,360 --> 01:01:55,933
不知道事后洛基会如何处置博士
I dread what he plans for him once he's done.

1014
01:01:56,071 --> 01:01:57,185
艾力是个好人
Erik is a good man.

1015
01:01:57,322 --> 01:01:58,317
他经常提及你
He talks about you a lot.

1016
01:02:00,200 --> 01:02:02,192
你改变了他一生
You changed his life.

1017
01:02:03,912 --> 01:02:05,785
你也改变了这里一切
You changed everything around here.

1018
01:02:05,914 --> 01:02:08,036
还是原来的好
They were better as they were.

1019
01:02:08,625 --> 01:02:10,700
在永恒国度，我们自命不凡
We pretend on Asgard that we're more advanced

1020
01:02:10,836 --> 01:02:14,536
来到凡间却如巨兽
but we come here, battling like bilge snipe.

1021
01:02:14,673 --> 01:02:16,499
- 什么？ - 巨兽
- Like what? - Bilge snipe.

1022
01:02:16,633 --> 01:02:19,669
巨型，有鳞，有鹿角
You know, huge, scaly, big antlers.

1023
01:02:20,471 --> 01:02:22,261
- 这里没有吧？ - 应该没有
- You don't have those? - I don't think so.

1024
01:02:22,389 --> 01:02:24,262
它们很讨厌
Well, they are repulsive.

1025
01:02:25,601 --> 01:02:27,842
它们践踏所经之处
And they trample everything in their path.

1026
01:02:35,527 --> 01:02:38,860
我首次来地球时，亦使洛基迁怒于此
When I first came to Earth, Loki's rage followed me here,

1027
01:02:38,989 --> 01:02:41,313
人类损失惨重
and your people paid the price.

1028
01:02:41,450 --> 01:02:43,240
如今历史再现
And now, again.

1029
01:02:45,787 --> 01:02:48,241
年壮时我热衷战斗
In my youth, I courted war.

1030
01:02:49,999 --> 01:02:51,991
战争还没有开始
War hasn't started yet.

1031
01:02:53,127 --> 01:02:54,918
你认为你可以令洛基告诉我们
You think you could make Loki tell us

1032
01:02:55,046 --> 01:02:56,325
立方在哪吗？
where the Tesseract is?

1033
01:02:56,464 --> 01:02:59,713
洛基深不可测
I do not know. Loki's mind is far afield.

1034
01:02:59,842 --> 01:03:04,550
他不但要权力，还要报复我
It's not just power he craves, it's vengeance, upon me.

1035
01:03:04,680 --> 01:03:06,802
为求达到目的，他会不择手段
There's no pain would prise his need from him.

1036
01:03:07,892 --> 01:03:11,721
简直不知天高地厚
A lot of guys think that until the pain starts.

1037
01:03:14,023 --> 01:03:15,516
你有何吩咐
What are you asking me to do?

1038
01:03:15,650 --> 01:03:19,232
那你有何计划？
I'm asking, what are you prepared to do?

1039
01:03:19,362 --> 01:03:20,392
洛基已是阶下囚
Loki is a prisoner.

1040
01:03:20,530 --> 01:03:24,567
为何我觉得他才是唯一想留在船上的人？
Then why do I feel like he's the only person on this boat that wants to be here?

1041
01:03:37,171 --> 01:03:40,255
可以潜近我身边的人不多
There's not many people who can sneak up on me.

1042
01:03:40,383 --> 01:03:42,042
你猜到是我了
But you figured I'd come.

1043
01:03:42,718 --> 01:03:44,295
不过
After.

1044
01:03:45,179 --> 01:03:48,594
应该是在局长折磨我后
After whatever tortures Fury can concoct,

1045
01:03:48,724 --> 01:03:52,389
你会如知己般出现，安慰我
you would appear as a friend, as a balm.

1046
01:03:53,354 --> 01:03:55,013
接着我就会同你合作
And I would cooperate.

1047
01:03:55,148 --> 01:03:57,139
你对巴顿特工做过什么？
I want to know what you've done to Agent Barton.

1048
01:03:57,275 --> 01:03:59,266
我只是打开他心境
I would say I've expanded his mind.

1049
01:04:01,863 --> 01:04:03,771
那你赢得一切后
And once you've won,

1050
01:04:04,657 --> 01:04:05,937
成为众神之王以后
once you're king of the mountain,

1051
01:04:08,077 --> 01:04:10,567
会如何处置他？
what happens to his mind?

1052
01:04:10,473 --> 01:04:11,474


1053
01:04:11,831 --> 01:04:13,621
爱之心切吗？
Is this love, Agent Romanoff?

1054
01:04:13,750 --> 01:04:16,584
爱是孩童玩意，我只是欠他人情
Love is for children. I owe him a debt.

1055
01:04:20,465 --> 01:04:22,337
告诉我
Tell me.

1056
01:04:26,679 --> 01:04:29,928
效力神盾局前
Before I worked for S.H.I.E.L.D... I, uh...

1057
01:04:32,351 --> 01:04:36,265
我已稍有名气
Well, I made a name for myself.

1058
01:04:36,397 --> 01:04:39,397
因为天赋异禀
I have a very specific skill set.

1059
01:04:39,525 --> 01:04:43,189
所以肆无忌惮
I didn't care who I used it for, or on.

1060
01:04:44,197 --> 01:04:47,695
因此上了神盾局的黑名单
I got on S.H.I.E.L.D.'s radar in a bad way.

1061
01:04:48,868 --> 01:04:51,784
巴顿特工奉命刺杀我
Agent Barton was sent to kill me.

1062
01:04:52,830 --> 01:04:54,371
但他没杀我
He made a different call.

1063
01:04:56,334 --> 01:04:59,369
若我答应放过他，你会如何报答？
And what will you do if I vow to spare him?

1064
01:04:59,754 --> 01:05:01,081
我不会放你出来的
Not let you out.

1065
01:05:01,214 --> 01:05:03,086
相当有趣
No, but I like this.

1066
01:05:04,008 --> 01:05:07,423
自身难保，你竟敢讨价还价
Your world in the balance, and you bargain for one man.

1067
01:05:07,553 --> 01:05:09,628
改朝换代是常有的事
Regimes fall every day.

1068
01:05:09,764 --> 01:05:12,301
我都不在乎，我是俄国人
I tend not to weep over that. I'm Russian.

1069
01:05:12,433 --> 01:05:13,428
曾是
Or I was.

1070
01:05:14,727 --> 01:05:16,386
现在呢？
And what are you now?

1071
01:05:16,854 --> 01:05:19,807
很简单
It's really not that complicated.

1072
01:05:19,941 --> 01:05:24,020
我要还清血债
I got red in my ledger, I'd like to wipe it out.

1073
01:05:25,028 --> 01:05:26,569
行吗？
Can you?

1074
01:05:27,906 --> 01:05:31,689
能还清吗？
Can you wipe out that much red?

1075
01:05:32,869 --> 01:05:34,660
得雷科夫的女儿
Dreykov's daughter,

1076
01:05:36,081 --> 01:05:37,907
圣保罗…
São Paulo,

1077
01:05:38,959 --> 01:05:41,449
医院失火事件？
the hospital fire?

1078
01:05:42,295 --> 01:05:44,667
巴顿已对我和盘托出
Barton told me everything.

1079
01:05:44,798 --> 01:05:47,881
你背负不少血债
Your ledger is dripping. It's gushing red

1080
01:05:48,009 --> 01:05:50,499
单凭拯救个不比你好多少的人
and you think saving a man no more virtuous than yourself

1081
01:05:50,637 --> 01:05:52,011
就可以令自己良心好过？
will change anything?

1082
01:05:52,139 --> 01:05:54,807
未免太过自以为是
This is the basest sentimentality.

1083
01:05:54,933 --> 01:05:57,174
简直幼稚
This is a child at prayer.

1084
01:05:57,310 --> 01:05:58,590
太可怜
Pathetic!

1085
01:05:59,396 --> 01:06:01,968
你满口胡言，杀戮无数
You lie and kill

1086
01:06:02,107 --> 01:06:05,142
助纣为虐
in the service of liars and killers.

1087
01:06:05,488 --> 01:06:07,427
（发现病毒 非法入侵）

1088
01:06:08,238 --> 01:06:14,237
你以为可以置身事外
You pretend to be separate,to have your own code,something that makes up for the horrors.

1089
01:06:15,412 --> 01:06:17,818
但江山易改
But they are part of you.

1090
01:06:17,956 --> 01:06:21,739
本性难移
And they will never go away.

1091
01:06:22,335 --> 01:06:25,834
巴顿没杀死你之前，我不会杀他
I won't touch Barton, not until I make him kill you.

1092
01:06:25,964 --> 01:06:28,205
我要他用尽你所恐惧的方式
Slowly, intimately,

1093
01:06:28,341 --> 01:06:30,713
驾轻就熟地杀死你
in every way he knows you fear.

1094
01:06:30,844 --> 01:06:33,927
当他苏醒时，见到自己的所为
And then he'll wake just long enough to see his good work

1095
01:06:34,055 --> 01:06:37,506
就会尖叫，而我会趁机取他首级
and when he screams, I'll split his skull.

1096
01:06:37,642 --> 01:06:40,761
这就是我的目的，哭吧，贱人
This is my bargain, you mewling quim.

1097
01:06:40,581 --> 01:06:41,999


1098
01:06:42,355 --> 01:06:43,932
怪物
You're a monster.

1099
01:06:44,794 --> 01:06:46,003


1100
01:06:46,087 --> 01:06:47,588
噢，不
Oh, no.

1101
01:06:48,528 --> 01:06:50,105
你带来的那个才是怪物
You brought the monster.

1102
01:06:53,116 --> 01:06:54,693
利用班纳
So, Banner.

1103
01:06:55,744 --> 01:06:56,905
这就是你的计划
That's your play.

1104
01:06:56,950 --> 01:06:57,951
什么？
What?

1105
01:06:59,039 --> 01:07:00,698
洛基计划利用班纳
Loki means to unleash the Hulk.

1106
01:07:00,832 --> 01:07:02,290
令班纳留在实验室，我马上过来
Keep Banner in the lab. I'm on my way.

1107
01:07:02,417 --> 01:07:03,495
顺道也让托尔过来
Send Thor as well.

1108
01:07:05,170 --> 01:07:06,497
多谢
Thank you

1109
01:07:06,630 --> 01:07:08,787
你的合作
for your cooperation.

1110
01:07:16,306 --> 01:07:17,764
干嘛，史塔先生
What are you doing, Mr. Stark?

1111
01:07:17,891 --> 01:07:20,381
我同你有一样的疑惑
Uh, kind of been wondering the same thing about you.

1112
01:07:20,519 --> 01:07:22,391
你本该追踪立方的位置
You're supposed to be locating the Tesseract.

1113
01:07:22,521 --> 01:07:24,097
没错，已经锁定位置
We are. The model's locked

1114
01:07:24,231 --> 01:07:25,510
正在匹配标记
and we're sweeping for the signature now.

1115
01:07:25,649 --> 01:07:26,644
顺利的话
When we get a hit,

1116
01:07:26,775 --> 01:07:28,731
就可以锁定目标于半公里范围内
we'll have the location within half a mile.

1117
01:07:28,860 --> 01:07:31,362
接着就可以拿回立方，别着急
Yeah, then you get your Cube back. No muss, no fuss.

1118
01:07:31,363 --> 01:07:33,105


1119
01:07:33,240 --> 01:07:34,353
何为「第二阶段」？
What is "Phase 2"?

1120
01:07:36,576 --> 01:07:39,410
第二阶段是神盾局会利用立方制作武器
Phase 2 is S.H.I.E.L.D. uses the Cube to make weapons.

1121
01:07:39,538 --> 01:07:41,280
对不起，电脑不如我反应快
Sorry, computer was moving a little slow for me.

1122
01:07:41,415 --> 01:07:44,118
罗杰斯，我们收集了所有有关立方的信息
Rogers, we gathered everything related to the Tesseract.

1123
01:07:44,251 --> 01:07:45,708
这不代表我们要制作…
This does not mean that we're making...

1124
01:07:45,836 --> 01:07:46,830
得了
I'm sorry, Nick.

1125
01:07:46,962 --> 01:07:49,249
你还想狡辩
What were you lying?

1126
01:07:49,381 --> 01:07:50,625
原来如此
I was wrong, Director.

1127
01:07:50,757 --> 01:07:51,787
世界还是没有改变
The world hasn't changed a bit.

1128
01:07:51,925 --> 01:07:52,955
你知情？
Did you know about this?

1129
01:07:53,093 --> 01:07:55,880
博士，你想离开这里吗？
You want to think about removing yourself from this environment, Doctor?

1130
01:07:56,012 --> 01:07:58,170
我在加尔各答时，也很想离开
I was in Calcutta. I was pretty well removed.

1131
01:07:58,306 --> 01:07:59,468
洛基在利用你
Loki is manipulating you.

1132
01:07:59,599 --> 01:08:01,176
那你呢？
And you've been doing what, exactly?

1133
01:08:01,309 --> 01:08:02,968
你不是因我对你抛媚眼而来这里
You didn't come here because I bat my eyelashes at you.

1134
01:08:03,103 --> 01:08:05,634
那我也不会因为你觉得不安而离开
Yes, and I'm not leaving because suddenly you get a little twitchy.

1135
01:08:05,772 --> 01:08:07,396
我想知道为什么
I'd like to know why S.H.I.E.L.D.

1136
01:08:07,523 --> 01:08:11,223
神盾局要利用立方来制作大杀伤力武器
is using the Tesseract to build weapons of mass destruction.

1137
01:08:11,861 --> 01:08:12,974
因为他
Because of him.

1138
01:08:14,280 --> 01:08:15,275
我？
Me?

1139
01:08:16,240 --> 01:08:18,611
去年，有异星客来访地球
Last year, Earth had a visitor from another planet

1140
01:08:18,743 --> 01:08:21,908
异星客间的斗争摧毁了一个小镇
who had a grudge match that leveled a small town.

1141
01:08:22,037 --> 01:08:24,243
我们才知道原来天外有生命
We learned that not only are we not alone

1142
01:08:24,373 --> 01:08:27,955
而且相较之下，人类简直不堪一击
but we are hopelessly, hilariously, outgunned.

1143
01:08:28,085 --> 01:08:30,326
我的臣民只想和你们和平共处
My people want nothing but peace with your planet.

1144
01:08:30,463 --> 01:08:32,419
你不是唯一的天外生命体
But you're not the only people out there, are you?

1145
01:08:32,548 --> 01:08:34,504
难保没有其他生命体威胁地球
And you're not the only threat.

1146
01:08:34,633 --> 01:08:37,799
正所谓一山还有一山高
The world's filling up with people who can't be matched,

1147
