but you better stop pretending to be a hero.

1200
01:10:43,596 --> 01:10:46,050
像你这样的英雄？
A hero? Like you?

1201
01:10:46,182 --> 01:10:48,220
你只是个实验品
You're a laboratory experiment, Rogers.

1202
