In case you needed to kill me.

1213
01:11:33,478 --> 01:11:36,394
不过那是不可能的，我曾试过
But you can't. I know, I tried.

1214
01:11:39,109 --> 01:11:42,025
最低潮时期，我万念俱灰
I got low. I didn't see an end.

1215
01:11:42,153 --> 01:11:46,613
我饮弹自尽，可绿巨人却吐出来
So, I put a bullet in my mouth, and the other guy spit it out.

1216
01:11:47,200 --> 01:11:48,397
所以我死不成
So I moved on.

1217
01:11:48,535 --> 01:11:51,369
