- Keep that engine down! - Yes, sir.

1263
01:13:48,112 --> 01:13:49,819
去关押区，等待监视器关闭
Detention, wait for cameras to go dark.

1264
01:13:49,947 --> 01:13:51,737
- 收到 - 跟紧
- Got it. - Stay close.

1265
01:13:53,492 --> 01:13:54,985
走，到第四层
Let's go, Level 4.

1266
01:13:55,953 --> 01:13:58,739
三号引擎，在那里碰头
Engine three. I'll meet you there.

1267
