1297
01:15:43,790 --> 01:15:45,125
- 谢谢
- Thanks.

1298
01:15:48,482 --> 01:15:49,644
史塔
Stark!

1299
01:15:52,361 --> 01:15:54,020
史塔，我来了
Stark, I'm here!

1300
01:15:54,092 --> 01:15:55,302
好
Good.

1301
01:15:56,865 --> 01:15:58,857
看下情况如何
Let's see what we've got.

1302
01:15:58,992 --> 01:16:00,651
我要让这个超导制冷系统
I got to get this superconducting coolant system

1303
01:16:00,786 --> 01:16:01,781
重运作
back online

1304
01:16:01,912 --> 01:16:03,370
接近回转轴前
before I can access the rotors,

1305
01:16:03,497 --> 01:16:05,323
我要清理残骸
work on dislodging the debris.

1306
