Superheroes in New York? Give me a break.

1984
02:10:15,604 --> 02:10:17,512
这般所谓的英雄
These so-called "heroes"

1985
02:10:17,648 --> 02:10:21,223
要对这所城市遭受的破坏负责
have to be held responsible for the destruction done to this city.

1986
02:10:21,359 --> 02:10:23,481
这是他们造成的，他们去哪了？
This was their fight. Where are they now?

1987
02:10:24,112 --> 02:10:26,436
尽管大家对这些英雄疑问多多
Tough questions are being asked about the Avengers themselves.

1988
02:10:26,572 --> 02:10:27,567
他们从天而降
Their sudden appearance

1989
02:10:27,698 --> 02:10:29,073
又突然消失
and equally sudden disappearance...

1990
02:10:29,200 --> 02:10:31,986
这也归咎于他们吗？
What, this is all somehow their fault?

1991
02:10:34,038 --> 02:10:37,204
美国队长救了我
Captain America saved my life.

1992
02:10:39,335 --> 02:10:42,833
无论他在哪里，无论他们在哪
Wherever he is, and wherever any of them are,

1993
02:10:42,964 --> 02:10:44,457
我只想…
I would just...

1994
02:10:45,258 --> 02:10:47,545
我只想道声谢
I would want to say thank you.

1995
02:10:50,012 --> 02:10:51,506
复仇者们去哪了？
Where are the Avengers?

1996
02:10:51,639 --> 02:10:54,046
我目前没追查他们的行踪
I'm not currently tracking their whereabouts.

1997
02:10:54,183 --> 02:10:56,341
但他们应该休息下
I'd say they've earned a leave of absence.

1998
02:10:56,477 --> 02:10:58,054
至于宇宙立方？
And the Tesseract?

1999
02:10:58,187 --> 02:11:00,428
立方回去了属于它的地方
The Tesseract is where it belongs.

2000
02:11:00,857 --> 02:11:03,181
一个我们去不到的地方
Out of our reach.

2001
02:11:03,317 --> 02:11:04,859
你无权话事
That's not your call.

2002
02:11:04,986 --> 02:11:06,016
我可没做什么
I didn't make it.

2003
02:11:06,154 --> 02:11:08,394
我只是遵循神的旨意
I just didn't argue with the god that did.

2004
02:11:08,531 --> 02:11:10,321
可你让他带走
So, you let him take it

2005
02:11:10,450 --> 02:11:12,073
至于战犯洛基
and the war criminal, Loki,

2006
02:11:12,201 --> 02:11:13,908
他应该为所犯下的负责
who should be answering for his crime.

2007
02:11:14,036 --> 02:11:16,609
他会的
Oh, I think he will be.

2008
02:11:30,094 --> 02:11:32,763
你根本不知道你在做什么
I don't think you understand what you've started,

2009
02:11:32,889 --> 02:11:35,343
对复仇者们放任不管
letting the Avengers loose on this world.

2010
02:11:35,892 --> 02:11:36,886
他们很危险的
They're dangerous.

2011
02:11:37,018 --> 02:11:40,682
全世界都知道
They surely are, and the whole world knows it.

2012
02:11:41,230 --> 02:11:43,803
全宇宙都知道
Every world knows it.

2013
02:11:44,233 --> 02:11:46,308
这就是你的目的？
Was that the point of all this?

2014
02:11:46,444 --> 02:11:48,186
声明？
A statement?

2015
02:11:50,907 --> 02:11:52,364
保证？
A promise.

2016
02:12:01,084 --> 02:12:02,625
长官，下一步怎么做？
Sir, how does it work now?

2017
02:12:03,753 --> 02:12:05,744
他们各奔天涯了
They've gone their separate ways.

2018
02:12:05,880 --> 02:12:08,797
有些还跑得相当远
Some, pretty extremely far.

2019
02:12:09,550 --> 02:12:11,459
如果再发生类似事件
If we get into a situation like this again,

2020
02:12:11,594 --> 02:12:13,135
要怎么办
what happens then?

2021
02:12:13,262 --> 02:12:14,257
他们会回来的
They'll come back.

2022
02:12:15,765 --> 02:12:17,472
你肯定？
Are you really sure about that?

2023
02:12:17,600 --> 02:12:18,595
没错
I am.

2024
02:12:20,228 --> 02:12:21,425
何以见得？
Why?

2025
02:12:22,480 --> 02:12:24,685
因为我们需要他们回来
Because we'll need them to.

2026
02:12:40,621 --> 02:12:42,372


2027
02:15:16,278 --> 02:15:18,768
人类
Humans.

2028
02:15:20,073 --> 02:15:24,402
并非我们想象中那么弱小
They are not the cowering wretches we were promised.

2029
02:15:25,370 --> 02:15:27,528
他们意志坚定
They stand.

2030
02:15:28,373 --> 02:15:34,825
桀骜不驯，因而难以奴役
They are unruly, and therefore cannot be ruled.

2031
02:15:41,803 --> 02:15:44,673
挑衅人类
To challenge them

2032
02:15:44,805 --> 02:15:48,505
等同自寻死路
is to court death.

2033
